851447,164,60,17,46,1,237,22,"Idha, bhikkhave , assutavā puthujjano– ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido ariyadhamme avinīto, sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido sappurisadhamme avinīto– manasikaraṇīye dhamme nappajānāti, amanasikaraṇīye dhamme nappajānāti. "
851448,164,60,47,73,1,175,23,"So manasikaraṇīye dhamme appajānanto amanasikaraṇīye dhamme appajānanto, ye dhammā na manasikaraṇīyā, te dhamme manasi karoti, ye dhammā manasikaraṇīyā te dhamme na manasi karoti."
851449,164,61,2,17,1,68,11,"‘ ‘ Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā na manasikaraṇīyā ye dhamme manasi karoti? "
