851478,164,65,42,54,1,58,10,‘ natthi me attā’ ti vā assa saccato thetato diṭṭhi uppajjati;
851479,164,65,55,68,1,70,10,‘ attanāva attānaṃ sañjānāmī’ ti vā assa saccato thetato diṭṭhi uppajjati;
851480,164,65,69,81,1,72,10,‘ attanāva anattānaṃ sañjānāmī’ ti vā assa saccato thetato diṭṭhi uppajjati;
851481,164,65,82,94,1,72,10,‘ anattanāva attānaṃ sañjānāmī’ ti vā assa saccato thetato diṭṭhi uppajjati; 
851482,164,65,95,101,1,32,6,atha vā panassa evaṃ diṭṭhi hoti–
851483,164,65,102,131,1,184,26,‘ yo me ayaṃ attā vado vedeyyo tatra tatra kalyāṇapāpakānaṃ kammānaṃ vipākaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti so kho pana me ayaṃ attā nicco dhuvo sassato avipariṇāmadhammo sassatisamaṃ tatheva ṭhassatī’ ti. 
851484,164,65,132,144,1,113,9,"Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave , diṭṭhigataṃ diṭṭhigahanaṃ diṭṭhikantāraṃ diṭṭhivisūkaṃ diṭṭhivipphanditaṃ diṭṭhisaṃyojanaṃ. "
851485,164,65,145,161,1,140,14,"Diṭṭhisaṃyojanasaṃyutto, bhikkhave, assutavā puthujjano na parimuccati jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi;"
851486,164,65,162,169,1,34,5,‘ na parimuccati dukkhasmā’ ti vadāmi. 
851487,164,66,2,36,1,230,23,"20.‘‘ Sutavā ca kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako– ariyānaṃ dassāvī ariyadhammassa kovido ariyadhamme suvinīto, sappurisānaṃ dassāvī sappurisadhammassa kovido sappurisadhamme suvinīto– manasikaraṇīye dhamme pajānāti amanasikaraṇīye dhamme pajānāti. "
851488,164,66,37,62,1,171,23,"So manasikaraṇīye dhamme pajānanto amanasikaraṇīye dhamme pajānanto ye dhammā na manasikaraṇīyā te dhamme na manasi karoti, ye dhammā manasikaraṇīyā te dhamme manasi karoti."
851489,164,67,2,17,1,71,12,"‘ ‘ Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā na manasikaraṇīyā ye dhamme na manasi karoti? "
851490,164,67,18,33,1,98,12,"Yassa, bhikkhave, dhamme manasikaroto anuppanno vā kāmāsavo uppajjati, uppanno vā kāmāsavo pavaḍḍhati; "
851491,164,67,34,43,1,64,8,"anuppanno vā bhavāsavo uppajjati, uppanno vā bhavāsavo pavaḍḍhati; "
851492,164,67,44,64,1,122,17,"anuppanno vā avijjāsavo uppajjati, uppanno vā avijjāsavo pavaḍḍhati– ime dhammā na manasikaraṇīyā, ye dhamme na manasi karoti."
851493,164,68,2,15,1,65,10,"‘ ‘ Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā manasikaraṇīyā ye dhamme manasi karoti? "
851494,164,68,16,32,1,99,13,"Yassa, bhikkhave, dhamme manasikaroto anuppanno vā kāmāsavo na uppajjati, uppanno vā kāmāsavo pahīyati; "
851495,164,68,33,44,1,65,9,"anuppanno vā bhavāsavo na uppajjati , uppanno vā bhavāsavo pahīyati; "
851496,164,68,45,63,1,117,16,"anuppanno vā avijjāsavo na uppajjati, uppanno vā avijjāsavo pahīyati– ime dhammā manasikaraṇīyā ye dhamme manasi karoti."
851497,164,69,2,21,1,147,17,"‘ ‘ Tassa amanasikaraṇīyānaṃ dhammānaṃ amanasikārā manasikaraṇīyānaṃ dhammānaṃ manasikārā anuppannā ceva āsavā na uppajjanti, uppannā ca āsavā pahīyanti. "
851498,164,70,2,47,1,184,26,"21.‘‘ So ‘ idaṃ dukkhan’ ti yoniso manasi karoti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ ti yoniso manasi karoti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ ti yoniso manasi karoti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yoniso manasi karoti. "
851499,164,70,48,61,1,100,10,"Tassa evaṃ yoniso manasikaroto tīṇi saṃyojanāni pahīyanti– sakkāyadiṭṭhi, vicikicchā, sīlabbataparāmāso. "
851500,164,70,62,70,1,46,6,"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, āsavā dassanā pahātabbā. "
851501,164,71,2,3,1,21,2,Saṃvarā pahātabbāsavā 
851502,164,72,2,16,1,43,6,"22.‘‘ Katame ca, bhikkhave, āsavā saṃvarā pahātabbā? "
851503,164,72,17,26,1,76,7,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu paṭisaṅkhā yoniso cakkhundriyasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati. "
851504,164,72,27,47,1,176,17,"Yañhissa, bhikkhave, cakkhundriyasaṃvaraṃ asaṃvutassa viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, cakkhundriyasaṃvaraṃ saṃvutassa viharato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. "
851505,164,72,48,72,1,201,16,Paṭisaṅkhā yoniso sotindriyasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati… pe… ghānindriyasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati… pe… jivhindriyasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati… pe… kāyindriyasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati… pe… manindriyasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati. 
851506,164,72,73,94,1,172,17,"Yañhissa, bhikkhave , manindriyasaṃvaraṃ asaṃvutassa viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, manindriyasaṃvaraṃ saṃvutassa viharato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti."
851507,164,73,2,25,1,152,18,"‘ ‘ Yañhissa, bhikkhave, saṃvaraṃ asaṃvutassa viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā , saṃvaraṃ saṃvutassa viharato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. "
