851509,164,74,2,3,1,24,2,Paṭisevanā pahātabbāsavā 
851510,164,75,2,16,1,46,6,"23.‘‘ Katame ca, bhikkhave, āsavā paṭisevanā pahātabbā? "
851511,164,75,17,26,1,59,7,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu paṭisaṅkhā yoniso cīvaraṃ paṭisevati–"
851512,164,75,27,53,1,140,10,"‘ yāvadeva sītassa paṭighātāya, uṇhassa paṭighātāya, ḍaṃsamakasavātātapasarīṃsapa-[ siriṃsapa( sī. syā. pī.)] samphassānaṃ paṭighātāya, yāvadeva hirikopīnappaṭicchādanatthaṃ’."
851513,164,76,2,8,1,39,5,‘ ‘ Paṭisaṅkhā yoniso piṇḍapātaṃ paṭisevati–
851514,164,76,9,59,1,246,31,"‘ neva davāya, na madāya, na maṇḍanāya, na vibhūsanāya, yāvadeva imassa kāyassa ṭhitiyā yāpanāya, vihiṃsūparatiyā, brahmacariyānuggahāya, iti purāṇañca vedanaṃ paṭihaṅkhāmi navañca vedanaṃ na uppādessāmi, yātrā ca me bhavissati anavajjatā ca phāsuvihāro ca’[ cāti( sī.)]."
851515,164,77,2,8,1,38,5,‘ ‘ Paṭisaṅkhā yoniso senāsanaṃ paṭisevati–
851516,164,77,9,23,1,151,9,"‘ yāvadeva sītassa paṭighātāya, uṇhassa paṭighātāya, ḍaṃsamakasavātātapasarīṃsapasamphassānaṃ paṭighātāya, yāvadeva utuparissayavinodanapaṭisallānārāmatthaṃ’."
851517,164,78,2,8,1,62,5,‘ ‘ Paṭisaṅkhā yoniso gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ paṭisevati–
851518,164,78,9,35,1,78,6,"‘ yāvadeva uppannānaṃ veyyābādhikānaṃ vedanānaṃ paṭighātāya, abyābajjhaparamatāya’[ abyāpajjhaparamatāya( sī. syā. pī.), abyāpajjaparamatāya( ka.)]."
851519,164,79,2,21,1,117,14,"‘ ‘ Yañhissa, bhikkhave, appaṭisevato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, paṭisevato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. "
851520,164,79,22,30,1,49,6,"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, āsavā paṭisevanā pahātabbā. "
