851538,164,89,2,3,1,21,2,Bhāvanā pahātabbāsavā 
851539,164,90,2,16,1,43,6,"27.‘‘ Katame ca, bhikkhave, āsavā bhāvanā pahātabbā? "
851540,164,90,17,30,1,130,11,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu paṭisaṅkhā yoniso satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ; "
851541,164,90,31,57,1,261,19,paṭisaṅkhā yoniso dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti… pe… vīriyasambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti… pītisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti… passaddhisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti… samādhisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti… upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ.
851542,164,91,2,21,1,114,14,"‘ ‘ Yañhissa, bhikkhave , abhāvayato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, bhāvayato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. "
851543,164,91,22,30,1,46,6,"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, āsavā bhāvanā pahātabbā. "
851544,164,92,2,78,1,407,60,"28.‘‘ Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ye āsavā dassanā pahātabbā te dassanā pahīnā honti, ye āsavā saṃvarā pahātabbā te saṃvarā pahīnā honti, ye āsavā paṭisevanā pahātabbā te paṭisevanā pahīnā honti, ye āsavā adhivāsanā pahātabbā te adhivāsanā pahīnā honti, ye āsavā parivajjanā pahātabbā te parivajjanā pahīnā honti, ye āsavā vinodanā pahātabbā te vinodanā pahīnā honti, ye āsavā bhāvanā pahātabbā te bhāvanā pahīnā honti; "
851545,164,92,79,83,1,22,3,"ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave–"
851546,164,92,84,119,1,122,12,"‘ bhikkhu sabbāsavasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati, acchecchi[ acchejji( ka.)] taṇhaṃ, vivattayi[ vāvattayi( sī. pī.)] saṃyojanaṃ, sammā mānābhisamayā antamakāsi dukkhassā’’’ ti. "
851547,164,93,2,4,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
851548,164,93,5,11,1,51,6,Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. 
851549,164,94,2,5,1,33,3,Sabbāsavasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dutiyaṃ.
851550,164,95,2,4,1,18,2,3 . Dhammadāyādasuttaṃ 
851551,164,96,2,20,1,87,11,29. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
851552,164,96,21,26,1,34,5,Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
851553,164,96,27,33,1,12,2,‘‘ bhikkhavo’’ ti.
851554,164,96,34,44,1,44,6,‘‘ Bhadante’’ ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. 
851555,164,96,45,47,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
851556,164,97,2,13,1,49,7,"‘ ‘ Dhammadāyādā me, bhikkhave, bhavatha, mā āmisadāyādā. "
851557,164,97,14,18,1,25,4,Atthi me tumhesu anukampā–
851558,164,97,19,30,1,56,8,"‘ kinti me sāvakā dhammadāyādā bhaveyyuṃ, no āmisadāyādā’ ti. "
851559,164,97,31,57,1,92,12,"Tumhe ca me, bhikkhave, āmisadāyādā bhaveyyātha no dhammadāyādā, tumhepi tena ādiyā[ ādissā( sī. syā. pī.)] bhaveyyātha–"
851560,164,97,58,67,1,53,6,"‘ āmisadāyādā satthusāvakā viharanti, no dhammadāyādā’ ti; "
851561,164,97,68,72,1,27,4,ahampi tena ādiyo bhaveyyaṃ–
851562,164,97,73,82,1,53,6,"‘ āmisadāyādā satthusāvakā viharanti, no dhammadāyādā’ ti. "
851563,164,97,83,100,1,95,13,"Tumhe ca me, bhikkhave, dhammadāyādā bhaveyyātha, no āmisadāyādā, tumhepi tena na ādiyā bhaveyyātha–"
851564,164,97,101,110,1,53,6,"‘ dhammadāyādā satthusāvakā viharanti, no āmisadāyādā’ ti; "
851565,164,97,111,116,1,30,5,ahampi tena na ādiyo bhaveyyaṃ–
851566,164,97,117,126,1,53,6,"‘ dhammadāyādā satthusāvakā viharanti, no āmisadāyādā’ ti. "
851567,164,97,127,137,1,59,7,"Tasmātiha me, bhikkhave, dhammadāyādā bhavatha, mā āmisadāyādā. "
851568,164,97,138,143,1,25,4,Atthi me tumhesu anukampā–
851569,164,97,144,155,1,56,8,"‘ kinti me sāvakā dhammadāyādā bhaveyyuṃ, no āmisadāyādā’ ti. "
851570,164,98,2,20,1,80,9,"30.‘‘ Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, bhuttāvī assaṃ pavārito paripuṇṇo pariyosito suhito yāvadattho; "
851571,164,98,21,38,1,51,6,siyā ca me piṇḍapāto atirekadhammo chaḍḍanīyadhammo[ chaḍḍiyadhammo( sī. syā. pī.)]. 
851572,164,98,39,55,1,53,6,Atha dve bhikkhū āgaccheyyuṃ jighacchādubbalya-[ jighacchādubballa( sī. pī.)] paretā . 
851573,164,98,56,59,1,20,3,Tyāhaṃ evaṃ vadeyyaṃ–
851574,164,98,60,72,1,78,9,"‘ ahaṃ khomhi, bhikkhave, bhuttāvī pavārito paripuṇṇo pariyosito suhito yāvadattho; "
851575,164,98,73,80,1,57,7,atthi ca me ayaṃ piṇḍapāto atirekadhammo chaḍḍanīyadhammo. 
851576,164,98,81,116,1,119,16,"Sace ākaṅkhatha, bhuñjatha, no ce tumhe bhuñjissatha[ sace tumhe na bhuñjissatha( sī. syā. pī.)], idānāhaṃ appaharite vā chaḍḍessāmi, appāṇake vā udake opilāpessāmī’ ti. "
851577,164,98,117,120,1,29,3,Tatrekassa bhikkhuno evamassa–
851578,164,98,121,130,1,68,8,‘ bhagavā kho bhuttāvī pavārito paripuṇṇo pariyosito suhito yāvadattho; 
851579,164,98,131,137,1,62,6,atthi cāyaṃ bhagavato piṇḍapāto atirekadhammo chaḍḍanīyadhammo. 
851580,164,98,138,155,1,96,13,"Sace mayaṃ na bhuñjissāma, idāni bhagavā appaharite vā chaḍḍessati, appāṇake vā udake opilāpessati’ . "
851581,164,98,156,160,1,28,4,Vuttaṃ kho panetaṃ bhagavatā–
851582,164,98,161,173,1,52,7,"‘ dhammadāyādā me, bhikkhave, bhavatha, mā āmisadāyādā’ ti. "
851583,164,98,174,180,1,43,5,"Āmisaññataraṃ kho panetaṃ, yadidaṃ piṇḍapāto. "
851584,164,98,181,201,1,103,11,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ imaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ abhuñjitvā imināva jighacchādubbalyena evaṃ imaṃ rattindivaṃ[ rattidivaṃ( ka.)] vītināmeyyan’’ ti. 
851585,164,98,202,212,1,88,10,So taṃ piṇḍapātaṃ abhuñjitvā teneva jighacchādubbalyena evaṃ taṃ rattindivaṃ vītināmeyya. 
851586,164,98,213,217,1,33,4,Atha dutiyassa bhikkhuno evamassa–
851587,164,98,218,227,1,68,8,‘ bhagavā kho bhuttāvī pavārito paripuṇṇo pariyosito suhito yāvadattho; 
851588,164,98,228,234,1,62,6,atthi cāyaṃ bhagavato piṇḍapāto atirekadhammo chaḍḍanīyadhammo. 
851589,164,98,235,251,1,96,13,"Sace mayaṃ na bhuñjissāma, idāni bhagavā appaharite vā chaḍḍessati, appāṇake vā udake opilāpessati. "
851590,164,98,252,275,1,107,11,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ imaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjitvā jighacchādubbalyaṃ paṭivinodetvā[ paṭivinetvā( sī. syā. pī.)] evaṃ imaṃ rattindivaṃ vītināmeyyan’ ti. 
851591,164,98,276,286,1,93,10,So taṃ piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjitvā jighacchādubbalyaṃ paṭivinodetvā evaṃ taṃ rattindivaṃ vītināmeyya. 
851592,164,98,287,313,1,182,23,"Kiñcāpi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu taṃ piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjitvā jighacchādubbalyaṃ paṭivinodetvā evaṃ taṃ rattindivaṃ vītināmeyya, atha kho asuyeva me purimo bhikkhu pujjataro ca pāsaṃsataro ca. "
