851751,164,124,2,4,1,25,2,Soḷasapariyāyaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ. 
851752,164,125,2,15,1,31,4,"49.‘‘ Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi–"
851753,164,125,16,48,1,263,28,‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ yā tā rattiyo abhiññātā abhilakkhitā– cātuddasī pañcadasī aṭṭhamī ca pakkhassa– tathārūpāsu rattīsu yāni tāni ārāmacetiyāni vanacetiyāni rukkhacetiyāni bhiṃsanakāni salomahaṃsāni tathārūpesu senāsanesu vihareyyaṃ appeva nāmāhaṃ bhayabheravaṃ passeyyan’ ti. 
851754,164,125,49,81,1,246,28,"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, aparena samayena yā tā rattiyo abhiññātā abhilakkhitā– cātuddasī pañcadasī aṭṭhamī ca pakkhassa– tathārūpāsu rattīsu yāni tāni ārāmacetiyāni vanacetiyāni rukkhacetiyāni bhiṃsanakāni salomahaṃsāni tathārūpesu senāsanesu viharāmi. "
851755,164,125,82,112,1,98,16,"Tattha ca me, brāhmaṇa, viharato mago vā āgacchati, moro vā kaṭṭhaṃ pāteti, vāto vā paṇṇakasaṭaṃ[ paṇṇasaṭaṃ( sī. pī.)] ereti; "
851756,164,125,113,129,1,31,4,tassa mayhaṃ brāhmaṇa etadahosi[ tassa mayhaṃ evaṃ hoti( sī. syā.)]–
851757,164,125,130,138,1,40,6,‘ etaṃ nūna taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchatī’ ti. 
851758,164,125,139,145,1,31,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi–"
851759,164,125,146,161,1,51,7,‘ kiṃ nu kho ahaṃ aññadatthu bhayapaṭikaṅkhī[ bhayapāṭikaṅkhī( sī.)] viharāmi? 
851760,164,125,162,197,1,126,13,"Yaṃnūnāhaṃ yathābhūtaṃ yathābhūtassa[ yathābhūtassa yathābhūtassa( sī. syā.)] me taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati, tathābhūtaṃ tathābhūtova[ yathābhūto yathābhūtova( sī. syā.)] taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivineyyan’ ti. "
851761,164,125,198,207,1,63,7,"Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, caṅkamantassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati. "
851762,164,125,208,228,1,111,16,"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva tiṭṭhāmi na nisīdāmi na nipajjāmi, yāva caṅkamantova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi. "
851763,164,125,229,238,1,58,7,"Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, ṭhitassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati. "
851764,164,125,239,252,1,65,11,"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva caṅkamāmi na nisīdāmi na nipajjāmi. "
851765,164,125,253,258,1,41,5,Yāva ṭhitova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi. 
851766,164,125,259,268,1,60,7,"Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, nisinnassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati. "
851767,164,125,269,289,1,109,16,"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva nipajjāmi na tiṭṭhāmi na caṅkamāmi, yāva nisinnova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi. "
851768,164,125,290,299,1,60,7,"Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, nipannassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati. "
851769,164,125,300,319,1,108,16,"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva nisīdāmi na tiṭṭhāmi na caṅkamāmi, yāva nipannova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi. "
851770,164,126,2,25,1,115,14,"50.‘‘ Santi kho pana, brāhmaṇa, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā rattiṃyeva samānaṃ divāti sañjānanti, divāyeva samānaṃ rattīti sañjānanti. "
851771,164,126,26,31,1,57,5,Idamahaṃ tesaṃ samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ sammohavihārasmiṃ vadāmi. 
851772,164,126,32,47,1,93,12,"Ahaṃ kho pana, brāhmaṇa, rattiṃyeva samānaṃ rattīti sañjānāmi, divāyeva samānaṃ divāti sañjānāmi. "
851773,164,126,48,57,1,43,7,"Yaṃ kho taṃ, brāhmaṇa, sammā vadamāno vadeyya–"
851774,164,126,58,78,1,153,17,"‘ asammohadhammo satto loke uppanno bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānan’ ti, mameva taṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya–"
851775,164,126,79,93,1,119,12,‘ asammohadhammo satto loke uppanno bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānan’ ti. 
851776,164,127,2,39,1,129,17,"51.‘‘ Āraddhaṃ kho pana me, brāhmaṇa, vīriyaṃ ahosi asallīnaṃ, upaṭṭhitā sati asammuṭṭhā[ appammuṭṭhā( syā.)], passaddho kāyo asāraddho, samāhitaṃ cittaṃ ekaggaṃ. "
851777,164,127,40,59,1,142,17,"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. "
851778,164,127,60,75,1,143,14,Vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. 
851779,164,127,76,89,1,86,12,"Pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca vihāsiṃ, sato ca sampajāno sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedesiṃ; "
851780,164,127,90,94,1,24,4,yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti–
851781,164,127,95,105,1,66,8,‘ upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ ti tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. 
851782,164,127,106,121,1,155,15,Sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. 
851783,164,128,2,23,1,155,15,52.‘‘ So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte pubbenivāsānussatiñāṇāya cittaṃ abhininnāmesiṃ. 
851784,164,128,24,62,1,325,34,"So anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarāmi, seyyathidaṃ– ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe–"
851785,164,128,63,77,1,122,12,"‘ amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ; "
851786,164,128,78,92,1,122,12,"tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ ti. "
851787,164,128,93,99,1,58,6,Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarāmi. 
851788,164,128,100,129,1,171,24,"Ayaṃ kho me, brāhmaṇa, rattiyā paṭhame yāme paṭhamā vijjā adhigatā, avijjā vihatā vijjā uppannā, tamo vihato āloko uppanno, yathā taṃ appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato. "
851789,164,129,2,24,1,156,16,53.‘‘ So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte sattānaṃ cutūpapātañāṇāya cittaṃ abhininnāmesiṃ. 
851790,164,129,25,43,1,160,18,So dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passāmi cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāmi–
851791,164,129,44,60,1,165,14,‘ ime vata bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā vacīduccaritena samannāgatā manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā micchādiṭṭhikā micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā; 
851792,164,129,61,71,1,72,10,te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā. 
851793,164,129,72,89,1,165,15,Ime vā pana bhonto sattā kāyasucaritena samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā; 
851794,164,129,90,101,1,62,10,te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā’ ti. 
851795,164,129,102,120,1,161,18,Iti dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passāmi cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāmi. 
851796,164,129,121,150,1,171,24,"Ayaṃ kho me, brāhmaṇa, rattiyā majjhime yāme dutiyā vijjā adhigatā, avijjā vihatā vijjā uppannā, tamo vihato āloko uppanno, yathā taṃ appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato. "
851797,164,130,2,25,1,151,16,54.‘‘ So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte āsavānaṃ khayañāṇāya cittaṃ abhininnāmesiṃ. 
851798,164,130,26,59,1,196,22,"So‘ idaṃ dukkhan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ,‘ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ."
851799,164,130,60,92,1,187,21,"‘ Ime āsavā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ,‘ ayaṃ āsavasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ,‘ ayaṃ āsavanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ,‘ ayaṃ āsavanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ. "
851800,164,130,93,110,1,126,15,"Tassa me evaṃ jānato evaṃ passato kāmāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccittha, bhavāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccittha, avijjāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccittha. "
