852254,164,229,2,87,1,396,36,"86.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, cunda, ye keci akusalā dhammā sabbe te adhobhāgaṅgamanīyā[ adhobhāvaṅgamanīyā( sī. syā. pī.)], ye keci kusalā dhammā sabbe te uparibhāgaṅgamanīyā[ uparibhāvaṅgamanīyā( sī. syā. pī.)], evameva kho, cunda, vihiṃsakassa purisapuggalassa avihiṃsā hoti uparibhāgāya[ uparibhāvāya( sī. syā. ka.)], pāṇātipātissa purisapuggalassa pāṇātipātā veramaṇī hoti uparibhāgāya… pe… sandiṭṭhiparāmāsi-ādhānaggāhi-duppaṭinissaggissa purisapuggalassa asandiṭṭhiparāmāsi-anādhānaggāhi-suppaṭinissaggitā hoti uparibhāgāya. "
852255,164,230,2,21,1,95,11,"87.‘‘ So vata, cunda, attanā palipapalipanno paraṃ palipapalipannaṃ uddharissatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
852256,164,230,22,35,1,94,10,"So vata, cunda, attanā apalipapalipanno paraṃ palipapalipannaṃ uddharissatīti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. "
