852310,164,237,2,4,1,17,2,9 . Sammādiṭṭhisuttaṃ 
852311,164,238,2,21,1,87,11,89. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
852312,164,238,22,28,1,43,6,Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi–
852313,164,238,29,36,1,18,3,‘‘ āvuso bhikkhave’’ ti.
852314,164,238,37,49,1,57,8,‘‘ Āvuso’’ ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. 
852315,164,238,50,53,1,26,3,Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca–
852316,164,239,2,22,1,40,6,"‘ ‘‘ Sammādiṭṭhi[ sammādiṭṭhī( sī. syā.)] sammādiṭṭhī’ ti, āvuso, vuccati. "
852317,164,239,23,46,1,129,16,"Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, ariyasāvako sammādiṭṭhi hoti, ujugatāssa diṭṭhi, dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgato, āgato imaṃ saddhamman’’ ti?"
852318,164,240,2,17,1,99,12,"‘ ‘ Dūratopi kho mayaṃ, āvuso, āgaccheyyāma āyasmato sāriputtassa santike etassa bhāsitassa atthamaññātuṃ. "
852319,164,240,18,25,1,68,7,Sādhu vatāyasmantaṃyeva sāriputtaṃ paṭibhātu etassa bhāsitassa attho. 
852320,164,240,26,34,1,50,6,Āyasmato sāriputtassa sutvā bhikkhū dhāressantī’’ ti.
852321,164,240,35,52,1,59,9,"‘‘ Tena hi, āvuso, suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī’’ ti."
852322,164,240,53,65,1,61,8,‘‘ Evamāvuso’’ ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. 
852323,164,240,66,69,1,26,3,Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca–
852324,164,241,2,43,1,237,27,"‘ ‘ Yato kho, āvuso, ariyasāvako akusalañca pajānāti, akusalamūlañca pajānāti, kusalañca pajānāti, kusalamūlañca pajānāti – ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, ariyasāvako sammādiṭṭhi hoti, ujugatāssa diṭṭhi, dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgato, āgato imaṃ saddhammaṃ. "
852325,164,241,44,57,1,82,9,"Katamaṃ panāvuso, akusalaṃ, katamaṃ akusalamūlaṃ, katamaṃ kusalaṃ, katamaṃ kusalamūlaṃ? "
852326,164,241,58,111,1,243,27,"Pāṇātipāto kho, āvuso, akusalaṃ, adinnādānaṃ akusalaṃ, kāmesumicchācāro akusalaṃ, musāvādo akusalaṃ, pisuṇā vācā[ pisuṇavācā( ka.)] akusalaṃ, pharusā vācā[ pharusavācā( ka.)] akusalaṃ, samphappalāpo akusalaṃ, abhijjhā akusalaṃ, byāpādo akusalaṃ, micchādiṭṭhi akusalaṃ– idaṃ vuccatāvuso akusalaṃ. "
852327,164,241,112,115,1,26,2,"Katamañcāvuso, akusalamūlaṃ? "
852328,164,241,116,129,1,84,9,"Lobho akusalamūlaṃ, doso akusalamūlaṃ, moho akusalamūlaṃ– idaṃ vuccatāvuso, akusalamūlaṃ."
852329,164,242,2,9,1,21,3,"‘ ‘ Katamañcāvuso , kusalaṃ? "
852330,164,242,10,53,1,294,32,"Pāṇātipātā veramaṇī kusalaṃ, adinnādānā veramaṇī kusalaṃ, kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇī kusalaṃ, musāvādā veramaṇī kusalaṃ, pisuṇāya vācāya veramaṇī kusalaṃ, pharusāya vācāya veramaṇī kusalaṃ, samphappalāpā veramaṇī kusalaṃ, anabhijjhā kusalaṃ, abyāpādo kusalaṃ, sammādiṭṭhi kusalaṃ– idaṃ vuccatāvuso, kusalaṃ. "
852331,164,242,54,57,1,25,2,"Katamañcāvuso, kusalamūlaṃ? "
852332,164,242,58,71,1,83,9,"Alobho kusalamūlaṃ, adoso kusalamūlaṃ, amoho kusalamūlaṃ– idaṃ vuccatāvuso, kusalamūlaṃ."
