852637,164,355,2,14,1,24,4,"121.‘‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, jāti? "
852638,164,355,15,37,1,151,19,"Yā tesaṃ tesaṃ sattānaṃ tamhi tamhi sattanikāye jāti sañjāti okkanti abhinibbatti khandhānaṃ pātubhāvo āyatanānaṃ paṭilābho, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, jāti. "
