853687,164,623,59,75,1,116,12,"‘ anissukī khomhi amaccharī’ ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
853688,164,624,2,14,1,68,9,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ–"
853689,164,624,15,23,1,29,6,‘ kiṃ nu khomhi saṭho māyāvī’ ti? 
853690,164,624,24,32,1,46,6,"Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti–"
853691,164,624,33,49,1,104,12,"‘ saṭho khomhi māyāvī’ ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
853692,164,624,50,57,1,49,6,"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti–"
853693,164,624,58,74,1,112,12,"‘ asaṭho khomhi amāyāvī’ ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
853694,164,625,2,15,1,68,9,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ –"
853695,164,625,16,24,1,32,6,‘ kiṃ nu khomhi thaddho atimānī’ ti? 
853696,164,625,25,33,1,46,6,"Sace, āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti–"
853697,164,625,34,50,1,107,12,"‘ thaddho khomhi atimānī’ ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
853698,164,625,51,58,1,49,6,"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti–"
853699,164,625,59,75,1,117,12,"‘ atthaddho khomhi anatimānī’ ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
853700,164,626,2,14,1,68,9,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhunā attanāva attānaṃ evaṃ paccavekkhitabbaṃ–"
853701,164,626,15,24,1,62,7,‘ kiṃ nu khomhi sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī’ ti? 
853702,164,626,25,34,1,46,6,"Sace, āvuso , bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti–"
853703,164,626,35,53,1,137,13,"‘ sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī khomhi ādhānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī’ ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
853704,164,626,54,61,1,49,6,"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti–"
853705,164,626,62,79,1,146,13,"‘ asandiṭṭhiparāmāsī khomhi anādhānaggāhī suppaṭinissaggī’ ti, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
853706,164,627,2,29,1,188,21,"‘ ‘ Sace , āvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme appahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā sabbesaṃyeva imesaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
853707,164,627,30,53,1,185,19,"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme pahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ, ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
853708,164,628,2,46,1,238,34,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, āvuso, itthī vā puriso vā, daharo yuvā maṇḍanajātiko, ādāse vā parisuddhe pariyodāte, acche vā udakapatte, sakaṃ mukhanimittaṃ paccavekkhamāno, sace tattha passati rajaṃ vā aṅgaṇaṃ vā, tasseva rajassa vā aṅgaṇassa vā pahānāya vāyamati; "
853709,164,628,47,59,1,61,11,"no ce tattha passati rajaṃ vā aṅgaṇaṃ vā, teneva attamano hoti–"
853710,164,628,60,70,1,36,7,"‘ lābhā vata me, parisuddhaṃ vata me’ ti. "
853711,164,628,71,97,1,200,22,"Evameva kho, āvuso, sace bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme appahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā sabbesaṃyeva imesaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ. "
853712,164,628,98,124,1,188,20,"Sace panāvuso, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno sabbepime pāpake akusale dhamme pahīne attani samanupassati, tenāvuso, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ, ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesū’’ ti. "
853713,164,629,2,4,1,29,2,Idamavocāyasmā mahāmoggallāno. 
853714,164,629,5,12,1,68,7,Attamanā te bhikkhū āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. 
853715,164,630,2,5,1,32,3,Anumānasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ.
853716,164,631,2,4,1,15,2,6 . Cetokhilasuttaṃ 
853717,164,632,2,22,1,87,11,185. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
853718,164,632,23,28,1,34,5,Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
853719,164,632,29,35,1,12,2,‘‘ bhikkhavo’’ ti.
853720,164,632,36,46,1,44,6,‘‘ Bhadante’’ ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. 
853721,164,632,47,49,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
853722,164,633,2,41,1,182,21,"‘ ‘ Yassa kassaci, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pañca cetokhilā appahīnā, pañca cetasovinibandhā[ cetasovinibaddhā( sī.), cetovinibaddhā( sāratthadīpanīṭīkā)] asamucchinnā, so vatimasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatīti– netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
853723,164,634,2,9,1,40,6,‘ ‘ Katamāssa pañca cetokhilā appahīnā honti? 
853724,164,634,10,21,1,81,9,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati. "
853725,164,634,22,42,1,144,18,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853726,164,634,43,57,1,105,13,"Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ paṭhamo cetokhilo appahīno hoti."
853727,164,635,2,24,1,133,17,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhamme kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati… pe… evamassāyaṃ dutiyo cetokhilo appahīno hoti."
853728,164,636,2,24,1,133,17,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saṅghe kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati… pe… evamassāyaṃ tatiyo cetokhilo appahīno hoti."
853729,164,637,2,16,1,89,11,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sikkhāya kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati. "
853730,164,637,17,39,1,144,18,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sikkhāya kaṅkhati vicikicchati nādhimuccati na sampasīdati, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853731,164,637,40,55,1,106,13,"Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ catuttho cetokhilo appahīno hoti."
853732,164,638,2,16,1,89,11,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīsu kupito hoti anattamano āhatacitto khilajāto. "
853733,164,638,17,38,1,144,18,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīsu kupito hoti anattamano āhatacitto khilajāto, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853734,164,638,39,54,1,105,13,"Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ pañcamo cetokhilo appahīno hoti. "
853735,164,638,55,60,1,37,5,Imāssa pañca cetokhilā appahīnā honti. 
853736,164,639,2,13,1,51,5,186.‘‘ Katamāssa pañca cetasovinibandhā asamucchinnā honti? 
853737,164,639,14,33,1,112,11,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāme avītarāgo[ avigatarāgo( katthaci)] hoti avigatacchando avigatapemo avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho. "
853738,164,639,34,57,1,175,20,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāme avītarāgo hoti avigatacchando avigatapemo avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853739,164,639,58,72,1,116,13,"Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ paṭhamo cetasovinibandho asamucchinno hoti."
853740,164,640,2,21,1,107,14,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye avītarāgo hoti… pe… evamassāyaṃ dutiyo cetasovinibandho asamucchinno hoti."
853741,164,641,2,23,1,107,14,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu rūpe avītarāgo hoti… pe… evamassāyaṃ tatiyo cetasovinibandho asamucchinno hoti."
853742,164,642,2,18,1,122,13,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yāvadatthaṃ udarāvadehakaṃ bhuñjitvā seyyasukhaṃ passasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ anuyutto viharati. "
853743,164,642,19,42,1,177,20,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yāvadatthaṃ udarāvadehakaṃ bhuñjitvā seyyasukhaṃ passasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ anuyutto viharati, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853744,164,642,43,57,1,117,13,"Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ catuttho cetasovinibandho asamucchinno hoti."
853745,164,643,2,16,1,83,10,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ devanikāyaṃ paṇidhāya brahmacariyaṃ carati–"
853746,164,643,17,34,1,93,15,‘ imināhaṃ sīlena vā vatena vā tapena vā brahmacariyena vā devo vā bhavissāmi devaññataro vā’ ti. 
853747,164,643,35,46,1,76,9,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ devanikāyaṃ paṇidhāya brahmacariyaṃ carati–"
853748,164,643,47,74,1,155,23,"‘ imināhaṃ sīlena vā vatena vā tapena vā brahmacariyena vā devo vā bhavissāmi devaññataro vā’ ti, tassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya . "
853749,164,643,75,89,1,116,13,"Yassa cittaṃ na namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ pañcamo cetasovinibandho asamucchinno hoti. "
853750,164,643,90,95,1,48,5,Imāssa pañca cetasovinibandhā asamucchinnā honti.
853751,164,644,2,31,1,190,23,"‘ ‘ Yassa kassaci, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ime pañca cetokhilā appahīnā, ime pañca cetasovinibandhā asamucchinnā, so vatimasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatīti– netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
853752,164,645,2,33,1,179,19,"187.‘‘ Yassa kassaci, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pañca cetokhilā pahīnā, pañca cetasovinibandhā susamucchinnā, so vatimasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatīti– ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
853753,164,646,2,9,1,38,6,‘ ‘ Katamāssa pañca cetokhilā pahīnā honti? 
853754,164,646,10,22,1,83,10,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari na kaṅkhati na vicikicchati adhimuccati sampasīdati. "
853755,164,646,23,44,1,143,18,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthari na kaṅkhati na vicikicchati adhimuccati sampasīdati, tassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853756,164,646,45,58,1,100,12,"Yassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ paṭhamo cetokhilo pahīno hoti."
853757,164,647,2,25,1,133,18,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhamme na kaṅkhati na vicikicchati adhimuccati sampasīdati… pe… evamassāyaṃ dutiyo cetokhilo pahīno hoti."
853758,164,648,2,25,1,133,18,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saṅghe na kaṅkhati na vicikicchati adhimuccati sampasīdati… pe… evamassāyaṃ tatiyo cetokhilo pahīno hoti."
853759,164,649,2,25,1,137,18,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sikkhāya na kaṅkhati na vicikicchati adhimuccati sampasīdati… pe… evamassāyaṃ catuttho cetokhilo pahīno hoti."
853760,164,650,2,28,1,98,13,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīsu na kupito hoti na anattamano[ attamano( sī. pī.)] anāhatacitto akhilajāto. "
853761,164,650,29,52,1,150,19,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīsu na kupito hoti na anattamano anāhatacitto akhilajāto, tassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853762,164,650,53,67,1,100,12,"Yassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ pañcamo cetokhilo pahīno hoti. "
853763,164,650,68,73,1,35,5,Imāssa pañca cetokhilā pahīnā honti. 
853764,164,651,2,14,1,52,5,188.‘‘ Katamāssa pañca cetasovinibandhā susamucchinnā honti? 
853765,164,651,15,28,1,106,11,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāme vītarāgo hoti vigatacchando vigatapemo vigatapipāso vigatapariḷāho vigatataṇho. "
853766,164,651,29,51,1,166,19,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāme vītarāgo hoti vigatacchando vigatapemo vigatapipāso vigatapariḷāho vigatataṇho, tassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853767,164,651,52,65,1,114,12,"Yassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ paṭhamo cetasovinibandho susamucchinno hoti."
853768,164,652,2,31,1,169,22,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye vītarāgo hoti… pe… rūpe vītarāgo hoti… pe… na yāvadatthaṃ udarāvadehakaṃ bhuñjitvā seyyasukhaṃ passasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ anuyutto viharati. "
853769,164,652,32,55,1,177,20,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na yāvadatthaṃ udarāvadehakaṃ bhuñjitvā seyyasukhaṃ passasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ anuyutto viharati, tassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853770,164,652,56,69,1,115,12,"Yassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ catuttho cetasovinibandho susamucchinno hoti."
853771,164,653,2,16,1,86,11,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na aññataraṃ devanikāyaṃ paṇidhāya brahmacariyaṃ carati–"
853772,164,653,17,35,1,93,15,‘ imināhaṃ sīlena vā vatena vā tapena vā brahmacariyena vā devo vā bhavissāmi devaññataro vā’ ti. 
853773,164,653,36,48,1,79,10,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na aññataraṃ devanikāyaṃ paṇidhāya brahmacariyaṃ carati–"
853774,164,653,49,74,1,152,22,"‘ imināhaṃ sīlena vā vatena vā tapena vā brahmacariyena vā devo vā bhavissāmi devaññataro vā’ ti, tassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya. "
853775,164,653,75,88,1,114,12,"Yassa cittaṃ namati ātappāya anuyogāya sātaccāya padhānāya, evamassāyaṃ pañcamo cetasovinibandho susamucchinno hoti. "
853776,164,653,89,94,1,49,5,Imāssa pañca cetasovinibandhā susamucchinnā honti.
853777,164,654,2,31,1,187,22,"‘ ‘ Yassa kassaci, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ime pañca cetokhilā pahīnā, ime pañca cetasovinibandhā susamucchinnā, so vatimasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatīti– ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. "
853778,164,655,2,28,1,262,15,"189.‘‘ So chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, vīriyasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, cittasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, ussoḷhīyeva pañcamī. "
853779,164,655,29,49,1,146,15,"Sa kho so, bhikkhave, evaṃ ussoḷhīpannarasaṅgasamannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo abhinibbidāya, bhabbo sambodhāya, bhabbo anuttarassa yogakkhemassa adhigamāya. "
853780,164,655,50,62,1,65,10,"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni aṭṭha vā dasa vā dvādasa vā. "
853781,164,655,63,71,1,75,8,Tānassu kukkuṭiyā sammā adhisayitāni sammā pariseditāni sammā paribhāvitāni. 
853782,164,655,72,79,1,48,7,Kiñcāpi tassā kukkuṭiyā na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya–
853783,164,655,80,95,1,112,12,‘ aho vatime kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjeyyun’ ti. 
853784,164,655,96,109,1,118,13,Atha kho bhabbāva te kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjituṃ. 
853785,164,655,110,131,1,151,15,"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, evaṃ ussoḷhipannarasaṅgasamannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo abhinibbidāya, bhabbo sambodhāya, bhabbo anuttarassa yogakkhemassa adhigamāyā’’ ti. "
853786,164,656,2,4,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
853787,164,656,5,11,1,51,6,Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. 
853788,164,657,2,5,1,34,3,Cetokhilasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ.
853789,164,658,2,4,1,16,2,7 . Vanapatthasuttaṃ 
853790,164,659,2,20,1,87,11,190. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
853791,164,659,21,26,1,34,5,Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
853792,164,659,27,33,1,12,2,‘‘ bhikkhavo’’ ti.
