853872,164,670,2,4,1,18,2,8 . Madhupiṇḍikasuttaṃ 
853873,164,671,2,19,1,81,10,199. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme. 
853874,164,671,20,29,1,89,9,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya kapilavatthuṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
853875,164,671,30,39,1,108,9,Kapilavatthusmiṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena mahāvanaṃ tenupasaṅkami divāvihārāya. 
853876,164,671,40,46,1,63,6,Mahāvanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā beluvalaṭṭhikāya mūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi. 
853877,164,671,47,63,1,93,9,Daṇḍapāṇipi kho sakko jaṅghāvihāraṃ[ jaṅghavihāraṃ( ka.)] anucaṅkamamāno anuvicaramāno yena mahāvanaṃ tenupasaṅkami. 
853878,164,671,64,71,1,69,7,Mahāvanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā yena beluvalaṭṭhikā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
853879,164,671,72,76,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
853880,164,671,77,84,1,73,7,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā daṇḍamolubbha ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
853881,164,671,85,92,1,57,7,Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho daṇḍapāṇi sakko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
853882,164,671,93,101,1,28,4,‘‘ kiṃvādī samaṇo kimakkhāyī’’ ti?
853883,164,671,102,148,1,294,35,"‘‘ Yathāvādī kho, āvuso, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya na kenaci loke viggayha tiṭṭhati, yathā ca pana kāmehi visaṃyuttaṃ viharantaṃ taṃ brāhmaṇaṃ akathaṃkathiṃ chinnakukkuccaṃ bhavābhave vītataṇhaṃ saññā nānusenti– evaṃvādī kho ahaṃ, āvuso, evamakkhāyī’’ ti."
853884,164,672,2,22,1,122,15,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ vutte daṇḍapāṇi sakko sīsaṃ okampetvā , jivhaṃ nillāḷetvā, tivisākhaṃ nalāṭikaṃ nalāṭe vuṭṭhāpetvā daṇḍamolubbha pakkāmi. "
853885,164,673,2,15,1,84,9,200. Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena nigrodhārāmo tenupasaṅkami; 
853886,164,673,16,20,1,35,4,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
853887,164,673,21,26,1,36,5,Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
853888,164,673,27,39,1,91,8,"‘‘ idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya kapilavatthuṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ. "
853889,164,673,40,49,1,109,9,Kapilavatthusmiṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena mahāvanaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃ divāvihārāya. 
