854840,164,814,2,14,1,52,7,"‘ ‘‘ Maṃsapesī’ ti kho, bhikkhu, nandīrāgassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
854841,164,814,15,20,1,36,4,"Ukkhipa maṃsapesiṃ, pajaha nandīrāgaṃ; "
854842,164,814,21,29,1,51,6,"abhikkhaṇa, sumedha, satthaṃ ādāyāti ayametassa attho."
854843,164,815,2,15,1,57,8,"‘ ‘‘ Nāgo’ ti kho, bhikkhu, khīṇāsavassetaṃ bhikkhuno adhivacanaṃ. "
854844,164,815,16,22,1,31,5,"Tiṭṭhatu nāgo, mā nāgaṃ ghaṭṭesi; "
854845,164,815,23,31,1,41,6,namo karohi nāgassāti ayametassa attho’’ ti. 
854846,164,816,2,4,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
854847,164,816,5,11,1,60,6,Attamano āyasmā kumārakassapo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. 
854848,164,817,2,5,1,31,3,Vammikasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ tatiyaṃ.
854849,164,818,2,4,1,17,2,4 . Rathavinītasuttaṃ 
854850,164,819,2,20,1,77,10,252. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
854851,164,819,21,31,1,94,10,Atha kho sambahulā jātibhūmakā bhikkhū jātibhūmiyaṃ vassaṃvuṭṭhā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
854852,164,819,32,37,1,57,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
854853,164,819,38,45,1,50,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho te bhikkhū bhagavā etadavoca–
854854,164,820,2,16,1,90,11,"‘ ‘ Ko nu kho, bhikkhave, jātibhūmiyaṃ jātibhūmakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ evaṃ sambhāvito–"
854855,164,820,17,100,1,705,68,"‘ attanā ca appiccho appicchakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca santuṭṭho santuṭṭhikathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca pavivitto pavivekakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca asaṃsaṭṭho asaṃsaggakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca āraddhavīriyo vīriyārambhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca sīlasampanno sīlasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca samādhisampanno samādhisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca paññāsampanno paññāsampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca vimuttisampanno vimuttisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca vimuttiñāṇadassanasampanno vimuttiñāṇadassanasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, ovādako viññāpako sandassako samādapako samuttejako sampahaṃsako sabrahmacārīnan’’’ ti?"
854856,164,820,101,117,1,108,11,"‘‘ Puṇṇo nāma, bhante, āyasmā mantāṇiputto jātibhūmiyaṃ jātibhūmakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ evaṃ sambhāvito–"
854857,164,820,118,143,1,159,18,"‘ attanā ca appiccho appicchakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā, attanā ca santuṭṭho… pe… ovādako viññāpako sandassako samādapako samuttejako sampahaṃsako sabrahmacārīnan’’’ ti. "
854858,164,821,2,16,1,70,10,253. Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā sāriputto bhagavato avidūre nisinno hoti. 
854859,164,821,17,22,1,40,5,Atha kho āyasmato sāriputtassa etadahosi–
854860,164,821,23,48,1,189,20,"‘‘ lābhā āyasmato puṇṇassa mantāṇiputtassa, suladdhalābhā āyasmato puṇṇassa mantāṇiputtassa, yassa viññū sabrahmacārī satthu sammukhā anumassa anumassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsanti, tañca satthā abbhanumodati. "
854861,164,821,49,77,1,133,16,"Appeva nāma mayampi kadāci karahaci āyasmatā puṇṇena mantāṇiputtena saddhiṃ samāgaccheyyāma[ samāgamaṃ gaccheyya( ka.)], appeva nāma siyā kocideva kathāsallāpo’’ ti. "
854862,164,822,2,18,1,85,11,254. Atha kho bhagavā rājagahe yathābhirantaṃ viharitvā yena sāvatthi tena cārikaṃ pakkāmi. 
854863,164,822,19,25,1,52,6,Anupubbena cārikaṃ caramāno yena sāvatthi tadavasari. 
854864,164,822,26,35,1,72,8,Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
854865,164,822,36,41,1,36,5,Assosi kho āyasmā puṇṇo mantāṇiputto–
854866,164,822,42,48,1,32,4,‘‘ bhagavā kira sāvatthiṃ anuppatto; 
854867,164,822,49,57,1,55,6,sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme’’ ti. 
854868,164,823,2,19,1,108,13,255. Atha kho āyasmā puṇṇo mantāṇiputto senāsanaṃ saṃsāmetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena sāvatthi tena cārikaṃ pakkāmi. 
854869,164,823,20,31,1,101,11,Anupubbena cārikaṃ caramāno yena sāvatthi jetavanaṃ anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāmo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
854870,164,823,32,37,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
854871,164,823,38,51,1,126,13,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ puṇṇaṃ mantāṇiputtaṃ bhagavā dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi. 
854872,164,823,52,77,1,248,25,Atha kho āyasmā puṇṇo mantāṇiputto bhagavatā dhammiyā kathāya sandassito samādapito samuttejito sampahaṃsito bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā yena andhavanaṃ tenupasaṅkami divāvihārāya. 
854873,164,824,2,13,1,59,7,256. Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; 
854874,164,824,14,18,1,45,4,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca–
854875,164,824,19,62,1,317,35,"‘‘ yassa kho tvaṃ, āvuso sāriputta, puṇṇassa nāma bhikkhuno mantāṇiputtassa abhiṇhaṃ kittayamāno ahosi, so bhagavatā dhammiyā kathāya sandassito samādapito samuttejito sampahaṃsito bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā yena andhavanaṃ tena pakkanto divāvihārāyā’’ ti. "
854876,164,825,2,17,1,125,14,Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto taramānarūpo nisīdanaṃ ādāya āyasmantaṃ puṇṇaṃ mantāṇiputtaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandhi sīsānulokī. 
854877,164,825,18,29,1,101,11,Atha kho āyasmā puṇṇo mantāṇiputto andhavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi. 
854878,164,825,30,40,1,89,9,Āyasmāpi kho sāriputto andhavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi. 
854879,164,826,2,14,1,104,11,Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenāyasmā puṇṇo mantāṇiputto tenupasaṅkami; 
854880,164,826,15,21,1,61,6,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā puṇṇena mantāṇiputtena saddhiṃ sammodi. 
854881,164,826,22,28,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
854882,164,826,29,38,1,80,9,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ puṇṇaṃ mantāṇiputtaṃ etadavoca– 
