854924,164,860,112,122,1,57,7,"Yathākathaṃ panāvuso, imassa bhāsitassa attho daṭṭhabbo’’ ti? "
854925,164,861,2,32,1,115,10,"258.‘‘ Sīlavisuddhiṃ ce, āvuso, bhagavā anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya, saupādānaṃyeva samānaṃ anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya[ paññāpessa( sī. syā.) evamaññatthapi]. "
854926,164,861,33,46,1,116,10,"Cittavisuddhiṃ ce, āvuso, bhagavā anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya, saupādānaṃyeva samānaṃ anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya. "
854927,164,861,47,60,1,117,10,"Diṭṭhivisuddhiṃ ce, āvuso, bhagavā anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya, saupādānaṃyeva samānaṃ anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya. "
854928,164,861,61,75,1,125,10,"Kaṅkhāvitaraṇavisuddhiṃ ce, āvuso, bhagavā anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya, saupādānaṃyeva samānaṃ anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya . "
