854931,164,861,104,118,1,122,10,"Ñāṇadassanavisuddhiṃ ce, āvuso, bhagavā anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya, saupādānaṃyeva samānaṃ anupādāparinibbānaṃ paññapeyya. "
854932,164,861,119,131,1,87,9,"Aññatra ce, āvuso, imehi dhammehi anupādāparinibbānaṃ abhavissa, puthujjano parinibbāyeyya. "
854933,164,861,132,140,1,42,6,"Puthujjano hi, āvuso, aññatra imehi dhammehi. "
