855168,164,900,22,31,1,85,9,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
855169,164,900,32,39,1,60,7,Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
