855171,164,900,45,57,1,57,8,"‘‘ cirassutā no, āvuso ānanda, bhagavato sammukhā dhammī kathā. "
855172,164,900,58,73,1,81,11,"Sādhu mayaṃ, āvuso ānanda, labheyyāma bhagavato sammukhā dhammiṃ kathaṃ savanāyā’’ ti."
855173,164,900,74,83,1,67,7,‘‘ Tena hāyasmanto yena rammakassa brāhmaṇassa assamo tenupasaṅkamatha; 
855174,164,900,84,95,1,69,9,appeva nāma labheyyātha bhagavato sammukhā dhammiṃ kathaṃ savanāyā’’ ti.
855175,164,900,96,108,1,58,8,‘‘ Evamāvuso’’ ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato ānandassa paccassosuṃ. 
855176,164,901,2,13,1,106,11,Atha kho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi–
855177,164,901,14,26,1,77,7,"‘‘ āyāmānanda, yena pubbārāmo migāramātupāsādo tenupasaṅkamissāma divāvihārāyā’’ ti."
