855242,164,914,66,79,1,69,8,"‘ icchāmahaṃ, āvuso kālāma, imasmiṃ dhammavinaye brahmacariyaṃ caritun’ ti. "
855243,164,914,80,89,1,47,7,"Evaṃ vutte, bhikkhave, āḷāro kālāmo maṃ etadavoca–"
855244,164,914,90,92,1,13,1,‘ viharatāyasmā; 
