855246,164,914,111,122,1,68,9,"So kho ahaṃ, bhikkhave, nacirasseva khippameva taṃ dhammaṃ pariyāpuṇiṃ. "
855247,164,914,123,146,1,154,18,"So kho ahaṃ, bhikkhave, tāvatakeneva oṭṭhapahatamattena lapitalāpanamattena ñāṇavādañca vadāmi theravādañca,‘ jānāmi passāmī’ ti ca paṭijānāmi ahañceva aññe ca. "
855248,164,914,147,153,1,32,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi–"
855249,164,914,154,169,1,114,14,‘ na kho āḷāro kālāmo imaṃ dhammaṃ kevalaṃ saddhāmattakena sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharāmīti pavedeti; 
