855254,164,915,49,59,1,59,7,"Evaṃ vutte, bhikkhave, āḷāro kālāmo ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ pavedesi. "
855255,164,915,60,66,1,32,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi–"
855256,164,915,67,77,1,60,8,"‘ na kho āḷārasseva kālāmassa atthi saddhā, mayhaṃpatthi saddhā; "
855257,164,915,78,87,1,62,8,"na kho āḷārasseva kālāmassa atthi vīriyaṃ, mayhaṃpatthi vīriyaṃ; "
