855689,164,1032,2,4,1,24,2,8 . Mahāhatthipadopamasuttaṃ 
855690,164,1033,2,21,1,87,11,300. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
855691,164,1033,22,28,1,43,6,Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi–
855692,164,1033,29,36,1,18,3,‘‘ āvuso bhikkhave’’ ti.
855693,164,1033,37,49,1,57,8,‘‘ Āvuso’’ ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. 
855694,164,1033,50,53,1,26,3,Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca–
855695,164,1033,54,76,1,157,17,"‘‘ seyyathāpi, āvuso, yāni kānici jaṅgalānaṃ pāṇānaṃ padajātāni sabbāni tāni hatthipade samodhānaṃ gacchanti, hatthipadaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati yadidaṃ mahantattena; "
855696,164,1033,77,91,1,86,12,"evameva kho, āvuso, ye keci kusalā dhammā sabbete catūsu ariyasaccesu saṅgahaṃ gacchanti. "
855697,164,1033,92,94,1,15,2,Katamesu catūsu? 
855698,164,1033,95,110,1,112,9,"Dukkhe ariyasacce , dukkhasamudaye ariyasacce, dukkhanirodhe ariyasacce, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ariyasacce’’. "
855699,164,1034,2,12,1,33,3,"301.‘‘ Katamañcāvuso, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ? "
855700,164,1034,13,30,1,124,13,"Jātipi dukkhā, jarāpi dukkhā, maraṇampi dukkhaṃ, sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsāpi dukkhā, yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ; "
855701,164,1034,31,35,1,38,3,"saṃkhittena, pañcupādānakkhandhā dukkhā. "
855702,164,1034,36,40,1,33,3,"Katame cāvuso, pañcupādānakkhandhā? "
855703,164,1034,41,52,1,116,6,"Seyyathidaṃ– rūpupādānakkhandho, vedanupādānakkhandho, saññupādānakkhandho, saṅkhārupādānakkhandho, viññāṇupādānakkhandho."
855704,164,1035,2,8,1,32,4,"‘ ‘ Katamo cāvuso, rūpupādānakkhandho? "
855705,164,1035,9,17,1,60,7,"Cattāri ca mahābhūtāni, catunnañca mahābhūtānaṃ upādāya rūpaṃ."
855706,164,1036,2,9,1,31,5,"‘ ‘ Katamā cāvuso, cattāro mahābhūtā? "
855707,164,1036,10,18,1,41,4,"Pathavīdhātu, āpodhātu , tejodhātu, vāyodhātu. "
855708,164,1037,2,12,1,26,3,"302.‘‘ Katamā cāvuso, pathavīdhātu? "
855709,164,1037,13,19,1,40,5,"Pathavīdhātu siyā ajjhattikā, siyā bāhirā. "
855710,164,1037,20,25,1,37,4,"Katamā cāvuso, ajjhattikā pathavīdhātu? "
855711,164,1037,26,65,1,283,35,"Yaṃ ajjhattaṃ paccattaṃ kakkhaḷaṃ kharigataṃ upādinnaṃ, seyyathidaṃ– kesā lomā nakhā dantā taco maṃsaṃ nhāru aṭṭhi aṭṭhimiñjaṃ vakkaṃ hadayaṃ yakanaṃ kilomakaṃ pihakaṃ papphāsaṃ antaṃ antaguṇaṃ udariyaṃ karīsaṃ, yaṃ vā panaññampi kiñci ajjhattaṃ paccattaṃ kakkhaḷaṃ kharigataṃ upādinnaṃ. "
855712,164,1037,66,71,1,40,4,"Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, ajjhattikā pathavīdhātu. "
855713,164,1037,72,85,1,85,11,"Yā ceva kho pana ajjhattikā pathavīdhātu, yā ca bāhirā pathavīdhātu, pathavīdhāturevesā."
855714,164,1037,86,103,1,88,12,"‘ Taṃ netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ ti– evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
855715,164,1037,104,114,1,97,9,"Evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā pathavīdhātuyā nibbindati, pathavīdhātuyā cittaṃ virājeti."
855716,164,1038,2,24,1,54,10,"‘ ‘ Hoti kho so, āvuso, samayo yaṃ bāhirā āpodhātu pakuppati[ pathavīdhātu pakuppati( ka.)]. "
855717,164,1038,25,31,1,49,6,Antarahitā tasmiṃ samaye bāhirā pathavīdhātu hoti. 
