856375,164,1131,77,84,1,60,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
856376,164,1131,85,99,1,85,10,"‘‘ addasaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, āyasmantañca revataṃ āyasmantañca ānandaṃ dūratova āgacchante. "
856377,164,1131,100,105,1,37,4,Disvāna āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavocaṃ–
856378,164,1131,106,111,1,21,4,‘ etu kho āyasmā ānando! 
856379,164,1131,112,119,1,77,7,Svāgataṃ āyasmato ānandassa bhagavato upaṭṭhākassa bhagavato santikāvacarassa! 
