856461,164,1140,2,4,1,18,2,3 . Mahāgopālakasuttaṃ 
856462,164,1141,2,21,1,87,11,346. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
856463,164,1141,22,27,1,34,5,Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
856464,164,1141,28,34,1,12,2,‘‘ bhikkhavo’’ ti.
856465,164,1141,35,45,1,44,6,‘‘ Bhadante’’ ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. 
856466,164,1141,46,48,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
856467,164,1142,2,33,1,88,11,"‘ ‘ Ekādasahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato gopālako abhabbo gogaṇaṃ pariharituṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ[ phātikattuṃ( sī. pī.), phātikātuṃ( syā. kaṃ.)]. "
856468,164,1142,34,36,1,18,2,Katamehi ekādasahi? 
856469,164,1142,37,96,1,228,36,"Idha, bhikkhave, gopālako na rūpaññū hoti, na lakkhaṇakusalo hoti, na āsāṭikaṃ hāretā[ sāṭetā( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] hoti, na vaṇaṃ paṭicchādetā hoti, na dhūmaṃ kattā hoti, na titthaṃ jānāti, na pītaṃ jānāti, na vīthiṃ jānāti, na gocarakusalo hoti anavasesadohī ca hoti. "
856470,164,1142,97,107,1,66,10,Ye te usabhā gopitaro gopariṇāyakā te na atirekapūjāya pūjetā hoti. 
856471,164,1142,108,122,1,98,12,"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, ekādasahi aṅgehi samannāgato gopālako abhabbo gogaṇaṃ pariharituṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ. "
856472,164,1142,123,140,1,125,14,"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ekādasahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjituṃ. "
856473,164,1142,141,143,1,18,2,Katamehi ekādasahi? 
856474,164,1142,144,191,1,227,36,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na rūpaññū hoti, na lakkhaṇakusalo hoti, na āsāṭikaṃ hāretā hoti, na vaṇaṃ paṭicchādetā hoti, na dhūmaṃ kattā hoti, na titthaṃ jānāti, na pītaṃ jānāti, na vīthiṃ jānāti, na gocarakusalo hoti, anavasesadohī ca hoti. "
856475,164,1142,192,206,1,104,13,Ye te bhikkhū therā rattaññū cirapabbajitā saṅghapitaro saṅghapariṇāyakā te na atirekapūjāya pūjetā hoti. 
856476,164,1143,2,16,1,42,6,"347.‘‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na rūpaññū hoti? "
856477,164,1143,17,38,1,135,16,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yaṃ kiñci rūpaṃ sabbaṃ rūpaṃ‘ cattāri mahābhūtāni, catunnañca mahābhūtānaṃ upādāyarūpan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
856478,164,1143,39,48,1,42,7,"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na rūpaññū hoti."
856479,164,1144,2,12,1,49,7,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na lakkhaṇakusalo hoti? "
856480,164,1144,13,29,1,90,10,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu‘ kammalakkhaṇo bālo, kammalakkhaṇo paṇḍito’ ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
856481,164,1144,30,39,1,49,7,"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na lakkhaṇakusalo hoti."
856482,164,1145,2,13,1,50,8,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na āsāṭikaṃ hāretā hoti? "
856483,164,1145,14,32,1,116,15,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannaṃ kāmavitakkaṃ adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantī karoti na anabhāvaṃ gameti. "
856484,164,1145,33,59,1,163,20,"Uppannaṃ byāpādavitakkaṃ… pe… uppannaṃ vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ… pe… uppannuppanne pāpake akusale dhamme adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantī karoti na anabhāvaṃ gameti. "
