856793,164,1213,152,170,1,134,12,"Evaṃ vimuttacitto kho, aggivessana, bhikkhu tīhi anuttariyehi samannāgato hoti– dassanānuttariyena, paṭipadānuttariyena, vimuttānuttariyena. "
856794,164,1213,171,222,1,314,42,"Evaṃ vimuttacitto kho, aggivessana, bhikkhu tathāgataññeva sakkaroti garuṃ karoti māneti pūjeti– buddho so bhagavā bodhāya dhammaṃ deseti, danto so bhagavā damathāya dhammaṃ deseti, santo so bhagavā samathāya dhammaṃ deseti, tiṇṇo so bhagavā taraṇāya dhammaṃ deseti, parinibbuto so bhagavā parinibbānāya dhammaṃ desetī’’ ti. "
856795,164,1214,2,14,1,54,6,"362. Evaṃ vutte, saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca –"
856796,164,1214,15,35,1,102,14,"‘‘ mayameva, bho gotama, dhaṃsī, mayaṃ pagabbā, ye mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ vādena vādaṃ āsādetabbaṃ amaññimha. "
856797,164,1214,36,56,1,126,17,"Siyā hi, bho gotama, hatthiṃ pabhinnaṃ āsajja purisassa sotthibhāvo, na tveva bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ āsajja siyā purisassa sotthibhāvo. "
856798,164,1214,57,87,1,133,17,"Siyā hi, bho gotama, pajjalitaṃ[ jalantaṃ( sī. pī.)] aggikkhandhaṃ āsajja purisassa sotthibhāvo , na tveva bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ āsajja siyā purisassa sotthibhāvo. "
856799,164,1214,88,108,1,128,17,"Siyā hi, bho gotama, āsīvisaṃ ghoravisaṃ āsajja purisassa sotthibhāvo, na tveva bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ āsajja siyā purisassa sotthibhāvo. "
856800,164,1214,109,127,1,102,14,"Mayameva, bho gotama, dhaṃsī, mayaṃ pagabbā, ye mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ vādena vādaṃ āsādetabbaṃ amaññimha. "
856801,164,1214,128,149,1,72,9,Adhivāsetu[ adhivāsetu ca( pī. ka.)] me bhavaṃ gotamo svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā’’ ti. 
856802,164,1214,150,153,1,31,3,Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. 
856803,164,1215,2,16,1,81,10,363. Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā te licchavī āmantesi–
856804,164,1215,17,33,1,87,11,"‘‘ suṇantu me bhonto licchavī, samaṇo me gotamo nimantito svātanāya saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena. "
856805,164,1215,34,43,1,55,7,Tena me abhihareyyātha yamassa patirūpaṃ maññeyyāthā’’ ti. 
856806,164,1215,44,57,1,127,13,Atha kho te licchavī tassā rattiyā accayena saccakassa nigaṇṭhaputtassa pañcamattāni thālipākasatāni bhattābhihāraṃ abhihariṃsu. 
856807,164,1215,58,70,1,103,12,Atha kho nigaṇṭhaputto sake ārāme paṇītaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ paṭiyādāpetvā bhagavato kālaṃ ārocāpesi–
856808,164,1215,71,83,1,36,6,"‘‘ kālo, bho gotama, niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan’’ ti. "
856809,164,1215,84,95,1,113,11,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena saccakassa nigaṇṭhaputtassa ārāmo tenupasaṅkami; 
856810,164,1215,96,102,1,59,6,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena. 
856811,164,1215,103,115,1,126,12,Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi. 
856812,164,1215,116,129,1,116,13,Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavantaṃ bhuttāviṃ onītapattapāṇiṃ aññataraṃ nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
856813,164,1215,130,137,1,65,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
856814,164,1215,138,156,1,75,12,"‘‘ yamidaṃ, bho gotama, dāne puññañca puññamahī ca taṃ dāyakānaṃ sukhāya hotū’’ ti."
856815,164,1215,157,175,1,105,12,"‘‘ Yaṃ kho, aggivessana, tādisaṃ dakkhiṇeyyaṃ āgamma avītarāgaṃ avītadosaṃ avītamohaṃ, taṃ dāyakānaṃ bhavissati. "
856816,164,1215,176,194,1,102,13,"Yaṃ kho, aggivessana, mādisaṃ dakkhiṇeyyaṃ āgamma vītarāgaṃ vītadosaṃ vītamohaṃ, taṃ tuyhaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti. "
856817,164,1216,2,5,1,36,3,Cūḷasaccakasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ.
856818,164,1217,2,4,1,17,2,6 . Mahāsaccakasuttaṃ 
856819,164,1218,2,19,1,78,10,364. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ. 
856820,164,1218,20,44,1,109,12,Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ sunivattho hoti pattacīvaramādāya vesāliṃ piṇḍāya pavisitukāmo[ pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya… pavisitukāmo hoti( sī.)]. 
856821,164,1218,45,56,1,115,11,Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto jaṅghāvihāraṃ anucaṅkamamāno anuvicaramāno yena mahāvanaṃ kūṭāgārasālā tenupasaṅkami. 
856822,164,1218,57,65,1,69,8,Addasā kho āyasmā ānando saccakaṃ nigaṇṭhaputtaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. 
856823,164,1218,66,69,1,29,3,Disvāna bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
856824,164,1218,70,84,1,96,9,"‘‘ ayaṃ, bhante, saccako nigaṇṭhaputto āgacchati bhassappavādako paṇḍitavādo sādhusammato bahujanassa. "
856825,164,1218,85,98,1,77,9,"Eso kho, bhante, avaṇṇakāmo buddhassa, avaṇṇakāmo dhammassa, avaṇṇakāmo saṅghassa. "
856826,164,1218,99,111,1,59,8,"Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā muhuttaṃ nisīdatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’ ti. "
856827,164,1218,112,116,1,29,4,Nisīdi bhagavā paññatte āsane. 
856828,164,1218,117,124,1,57,7,Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
856829,164,1218,125,136,1,98,10,"upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi, sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
856830,164,1218,137,144,1,65,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca– 
856831,164,1219,2,20,1,89,9,"365.‘‘ Santi, bho gotama, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kāyabhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti, no cittabhāvanaṃ. "
856832,164,1219,21,31,1,51,8,"Phusanti hi te, bho gotama, sārīrikaṃ dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ. "
856833,164,1219,32,68,1,194,21,"Bhūtapubbaṃ, bho gotama, sārīrikāya dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭhassa sato ūrukkhambhopi nāma bhavissati, hadayampi nāma phalissati, uṇhampi lohitaṃ mukhato uggamissati, ummādampi pāpuṇissati[ pāpuṇissanti( syā. kaṃ.)] cittakkhepaṃ. "
856834,164,1219,69,83,1,71,11,"Tassa kho etaṃ, bho gotama, kāyanvayaṃ cittaṃ hoti, kāyassa vasena vattati. "
856835,164,1219,84,87,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
856836,164,1219,88,91,1,20,2,Abhāvitattā cittassa. 
856837,164,1219,92,105,1,94,10,"Santi pana, bho gotama, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā cittabhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti, no kāyabhāvanaṃ. "
856838,164,1219,106,116,1,51,8,"Phusanti hi te, bho gotama, cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ. "
856839,164,1219,117,143,1,194,21,"Bhūtapubbaṃ, bho gotama, cetasikāya dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭhassa sato ūrukkhambhopi nāma bhavissati, hadayampi nāma phalissati, uṇhampi lohitaṃ mukhato uggamissati, ummādampi pāpuṇissati cittakkhepaṃ. "
856840,164,1219,144,158,1,69,11,"Tassa kho eso, bho gotama, cittanvayo kāyo hoti, cittassa vasena vattati. "
856841,164,1219,159,162,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
856842,164,1219,163,166,1,19,2,Abhāvitattā kāyassa . 
856843,164,1219,167,175,1,33,6,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bho gotama, evaṃ hoti–"
856844,164,1219,176,190,1,85,9,"‘ addhā bhoto gotamassa sāvakā cittabhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti, no kāyabhāvanan’’’ ti. "
856845,164,1220,2,19,1,45,7,"366.‘‘ Kinti pana te, aggivessana, kāyabhāvanā sutā’’ ti?"
856846,164,1220,20,115,1,523,66,"‘‘ Seyyathidaṃ– nando vaccho, kiso saṃkicco, makkhali gosālo– etehi, bho gotama, acelakā muttācārā hatthāpalekhanā naehibhaddantikā natiṭṭhabhaddantikā[ naehibhadantikā, natiṭṭhabhadantikā( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī. ka.)] na abhihaṭaṃ na uddissakataṃ na nimantanaṃ sādiyanti, te na kumbhimukhā paṭiggaṇhanti na kaḷopimukhā paṭiggaṇhanti na eḷakamantaraṃ na daṇḍamantaraṃ na musalamantaraṃ na dvinnaṃ bhuñjamānānaṃ na gabbhiniyā na pāyamānāya na purisantaragatāya na saṅkittīsu na yattha sā upaṭṭhito hoti na yattha makkhikā saṇḍasaṇḍacārinī , na macchaṃ na maṃsaṃ na suraṃ na merayaṃ na thusodakaṃ pivanti. "
856847,164,1220,116,133,1,96,14,"Te ekāgārikā vā honti ekālopikā, dvāgārikā vā honti dvālopikā… pe… sattāgārikā vā honti sattālopikā. "
856848,164,1220,134,147,1,77,10,"Ekissāpi dattiyā yāpenti, dvīhipi dattīhi yāpenti… pe… sattahipi dattīhi yāpenti. "
856849,164,1220,148,161,1,85,10,"Ekāhikampi āhāraṃ āhārenti, dvīhikampi āhāraṃ āhārenti… pe… sattāhikampi āhāraṃ āhārenti. "
856850,164,1220,162,170,1,77,6,Iti evarūpaṃ addhamāsikampi pariyāyabhattabhojanānuyogamanuyuttā viharantī’’ ti.
856851,164,1221,2,15,1,47,8,"‘ ‘ Kiṃ pana te, aggivessana, tāvatakeneva yāpentī’’ ti?"
856852,164,1221,16,23,1,19,4,"‘‘ No hidaṃ, bho gotama. "
856853,164,1221,24,48,1,158,19,"Appekadā, bho gotama, uḷārāni uḷārāni khādanīyāni khādanti, uḷārāni uḷārāni bhojanāni bhuñjanti, uḷārāni uḷārāni sāyanīyāni sāyanti, uḷārāni uḷārāni pānāni pivanti. "
856854,164,1221,49,64,1,62,11,"Te imaṃ kāyaṃ balaṃ gāhenti nāma, brūhenti nāma, medenti nāmā’’ ti."
856855,164,1222,2,20,1,92,14,"‘ ‘ Yaṃ kho te, aggivessana, purimaṃ pahāya pacchā upacinanti, evaṃ imassa kāyassa ācayāpacayo hoti. "
856856,164,1222,21,32,1,46,7,"Kinti pana te, aggivessana, cittabhāvanā sutā’’ ti? "
856857,164,1222,33,43,1,77,9,Cittabhāvanāya kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavatā puṭṭho samāno na sampāyāsi. 
856858,164,1223,2,12,1,50,6,367. Atha kho bhagavā saccakaṃ nigaṇṭhaputtaṃ etadavoca–
856859,164,1223,13,31,1,99,14,"‘‘ yāpi kho te esā, aggivessana, purimā kāyabhāvanā bhāsitā sāpi ariyassa vinaye no dhammikā kāyabhāvanā. "
856860,164,1223,32,60,1,84,11,"Kāyabhāvanampi[ kāyabhāvanaṃ hi( sī. pī. ka.)] kho tvaṃ, aggivessana, na aññāsi, kuto pana tvaṃ cittabhāvanaṃ jānissasi ? "
856861,164,1223,61,78,1,98,14,"Api ca, aggivessana, yathā abhāvitakāyo ca hoti abhāvitacitto ca, bhāvitakāyo ca hoti bhāvitacitto ca. "
856862,164,1223,79,90,1,47,7,"Taṃ suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi, bhāsissāmī’’ ti."
856863,164,1223,91,104,1,58,8,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavato paccassosi. "
856864,164,1223,105,107,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca– 
856865,164,1224,2,18,1,58,7,"368.‘‘ Kathañca , aggivessana, abhāvitakāyo ca hoti abhāvitacitto ca? "
856866,164,1224,19,28,1,64,7,"Idha, aggivessana, assutavato puthujjanassa uppajjati sukhā vedanā. "
856867,164,1224,29,39,1,80,10,So sukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno sukhasārāgī ca hoti sukhasārāgitañca āpajjati. 
856868,164,1224,40,45,1,32,5,Tassa sā sukhā vedanā nirujjhati. 
856869,164,1224,46,52,1,48,6,Sukhāya vedanāya nirodhā uppajjati dukkhā vedanā. 
856870,164,1224,53,65,1,98,12,So dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno socati kilamati paridevati urattāḷiṃ kandati sammohaṃ āpajjati. 
856871,164,1224,66,89,1,167,20,"Tassa kho esā, aggivessana, uppannāpi sukhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati abhāvitattā kāyassa, uppannāpi dukkhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati abhāvitattā cittassa. "
856872,164,1224,90,125,1,245,29,"Yassa kassaci, aggivessana, evaṃ ubhatopakkhaṃ uppannāpi sukhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati abhāvitattā kāyassa, uppannāpi dukkhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati abhāvitattā cittassa, evaṃ kho, aggivessana, abhāvitakāyo ca hoti abhāvitacitto ca. "
856873,164,1225,2,17,1,56,7,"369.‘‘ Kathañca, aggivessana, bhāvitakāyo ca hoti bhāvitacitto ca? "
856874,164,1225,18,27,1,63,7,"Idha, aggivessana, sutavato ariyasāvakassa uppajjati sukhā vedanā. "
856875,164,1225,28,42,1,86,12,"So sukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno na sukhasārāgī ca hoti, na sukhasārāgitañca āpajjati. "
856876,164,1225,43,48,1,32,5,Tassa sā sukhā vedanā nirujjhati. 
856877,164,1225,49,55,1,48,6,Sukhāya vedanāya nirodhā uppajjati dukkhā vedanā. 
856878,164,1225,56,73,1,113,17,So dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno na socati na kilamati na paridevati na urattāḷiṃ kandati na sammohaṃ āpajjati. 
856879,164,1225,74,99,1,171,22,"Tassa kho esā, aggivessana, uppannāpi sukhā vedanā cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati bhāvitattā kāyassa, uppannāpi dukkhā vedanā cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati bhāvitattā cittassa. "
856880,164,1225,100,127,1,190,23,"Yassa kassaci, aggivessana, evaṃ ubhatopakkhaṃ uppannāpi sukhā vedanā cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati bhāvitattā kāyassa, uppannāpi dukkhā vedanā cittaṃ na pariyādāya tiṭṭhati bhāvitattā cittassa. "
856881,164,1225,128,141,1,59,9,"Evaṃ kho, aggivessana, bhāvitakāyo ca hoti bhāvitacitto cā’’ ti. "
856882,164,1226,2,13,1,33,5,370.‘‘ Evaṃ pasanno ahaṃ bhoto gotamassa! 
856883,164,1226,14,25,1,54,8,Bhavañhi gotamo bhāvitakāyo ca hoti bhāvitacitto cā’’ ti .
856884,164,1226,26,46,1,85,14,"‘‘ Addhā kho te ayaṃ, aggivessana, āsajja upanīya vācā bhāsitā, api ca te ahaṃ byākarissāmi . "
856885,164,1226,47,96,1,245,33,"Yato kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito, taṃ vata me uppannā vā sukhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati, uppannā vā dukkhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ[ netaṃ khoṭhānaṃ( sī. pī.)] vijjatī’’ ti."
856886,164,1227,2,34,1,118,17,‘ ‘ Na hi nūna[ na hanūna( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] bhoto gotamassa uppajjati tathārūpā sukhā vedanā yathārūpā uppannā sukhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭheyya; 
856887,164,1227,35,55,1,123,17,na hi nūna bhoto gotamassa uppajjati tathārūpā dukkhā vedanā yathārūpā uppannā dukkhā vedanā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭheyyā’’ ti. 
856888,164,1228,2,13,1,25,4,"371.‘‘ Kiñhi no siyā, aggivessana? "
856889,164,1228,14,25,1,86,9,"Idha me, aggivessana, pubbeva sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi–"
856890,164,1228,26,33,1,47,5,"‘ sambādho gharāvāso rajāpatho, abbhokāso pabbajjā. "
856891,164,1228,34,43,1,106,9,Nayidaṃ sukaraṃ agāraṃ ajjhāvasatā ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ saṅkhalikhitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ. 
856892,164,1228,44,55,1,94,10,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajeyyan’ ti. 
856893,164,1228,56,87,1,242,26,"So kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, aparena samayena daharova samāno, susukāḷakeso bhadrena yobbanena samannāgato paṭhamena vayasā, akāmakānaṃ mātāpitūnaṃ assumukhānaṃ rudantānaṃ, kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajiṃ. "
856894,164,1228,88,100,1,111,12,So evaṃ pabbajito samāno kiṃkusalagavesī anuttaraṃ santivarapadaṃ pariyesamāno yena āḷāro kālāmo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; 
856895,164,1228,101,105,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā āḷāraṃ kālāmaṃ etadavocaṃ–
856896,164,1228,106,118,1,69,8,"‘ icchāmahaṃ, āvuso kālāma, imasmiṃ dhammavinaye brahmacariyaṃ caritun’ ti. "
856897,164,1228,119,128,1,49,7,"Evaṃ vutte, aggivessana, āḷāro kālāmo maṃ etadavoca–"
856898,164,1228,129,148,1,132,16,"‘ viharatāyasmā, tādiso ayaṃ dhammo yattha viññū puriso nacirasseva sakaṃ ācariyakaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyā’ ti. "
856899,164,1228,149,160,1,70,9,"So kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, nacirasseva khippameva taṃ dhammaṃ pariyāpuṇiṃ. "
856900,164,1228,161,186,1,156,18,"So kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, tāvatakeneva oṭṭhapahatamattena lapitalāpanamattena ñāṇavādañca vadāmi theravādañca,‘ jānāmi passāmī’ ti ca paṭijānāmi, ahañceva aññe ca. "
856901,164,1228,187,193,1,34,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, aggivessana, etadahosi–"
856902,164,1228,194,223,1,171,23,"‘ na kho āḷāro kālāmo imaṃ dhammaṃ kevalaṃ saddhāmattakena sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharāmīti pavedeti, addhā āḷāro kālāmo imaṃ dhammaṃ jānaṃ passaṃ viharatī’’’ ti."
856903,164,1229,2,13,1,57,8,"‘ ‘ Atha khvāhaṃ, aggivessana, yena āḷāro kālāmo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; "
856904,164,1229,14,19,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā āḷāraṃ kālāmaṃ etadavocaṃ–
856905,164,1229,20,37,1,99,13,"‘ kittāvatā no, āvuso kālāma, imaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharāmīti pavedesī’ ti? "
856906,164,1229,38,47,1,61,7,"Evaṃ vutte, aggivessana, āḷāro kālāmo ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ pavedesi. "
856907,164,1229,48,54,1,34,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, aggivessana, etadahosi–"
856908,164,1229,55,65,1,60,8,"‘ na kho āḷārasseva kālāmassa atthi saddhā, mayhaṃpatthi saddhā; "
856909,164,1229,66,75,1,62,8,"na kho āḷārasseva kālāmassa atthi vīriyaṃ, mayhaṃpatthi vīriyaṃ; "
856910,164,1229,76,85,1,56,8,"na kho āḷārasseva kālāmassa atthi sati, mayhaṃpatthi sati; "
856911,164,1229,86,95,1,62,8,"na kho āḷārasseva kālāmassa atthi samādhi, mayhaṃpatthi samādhi; "
856912,164,1229,96,105,1,58,8,"na kho āḷārasseva kālāmassa atthi paññā, mayhaṃpatthi paññā; "
856913,164,1229,106,123,1,138,16,yaṃnūnāhaṃ yaṃ dhammaṃ āḷāro kālāmo sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharāmīti pavedeti tassa dhammassa sacchikiriyāya padaheyyan’ ti. 
856914,164,1229,124,139,1,104,13,"So kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, nacirasseva khippameva taṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihāsiṃ."
856915,164,1230,2,13,1,57,8,"‘ ‘ Atha khvāhaṃ, aggivessana, yena āḷāro kālāmo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; "
856916,164,1230,14,18,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā āḷāraṃ kālāmaṃ etadavocaṃ–
856917,164,1230,19,36,1,87,12,"‘ ettāvatā no, āvuso kālāma , imaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja pavedesī’ ti?"
856918,164,1230,37,53,1,86,12,"‘ Ettāvatā kho ahaṃ, āvuso, imaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja pavedemī’ ti."
856919,164,1230,54,70,1,88,12,"‘ Ahampi kho, āvuso, ettāvatā imaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharāmī’ ti."
856920,164,1230,71,88,1,83,12,"‘ Lābhā no, āvuso, suladdhaṃ no, āvuso, ye mayaṃ āyasmantaṃ tādisaṃ sabrahmacāriṃ passāma. "
856921,164,1230,89,105,1,128,16,Iti yāhaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja pavedemi taṃ tvaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharasi; 
856922,164,1230,106,121,1,126,15,yaṃ tvaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharasi tamahaṃ dhammaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja pavedemi. 
856923,164,1230,122,130,1,48,8,Iti yāhaṃ dhammaṃ jānāmi taṃ tvaṃ dhammaṃ jānāsi; 
856924,164,1230,131,138,1,46,7,yaṃ tvaṃ dhammaṃ jānāsi tamahaṃ dhammaṃ jānāmi. 
856925,164,1230,139,149,1,53,9,"Iti yādiso ahaṃ tādiso tuvaṃ, yādiso tuvaṃ tādiso ahaṃ. "
856926,164,1230,150,162,1,52,9,"Ehi dāni, āvuso, ubhova santā imaṃ gaṇaṃ pariharāmā’ ti. "
856927,164,1230,163,200,1,126,19,"Iti kho, aggivessana, āḷāro kālāmo ācariyo me samāno( attano)[() natthi( sī. pī.)] antevāsiṃ maṃ samānaṃ attanā samasamaṃ ṭhapesi, uḷārāya ca maṃ pūjāya pūjesi. "
856928,164,1230,201,207,1,34,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, aggivessana, etadahosi–"
856929,164,1230,208,230,1,148,19,"‘ nāyaṃ dhammo nibbidāya na virāgāya na nirodhāya na upasamāya na abhiññāya na sambodhāya na nibbānāya saṃvattati, yāvadeva ākiñcaññāyatanūpapattiyā’ ti. "
856930,164,1230,231,244,1,81,11,"So kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, taṃ dhammaṃ analaṅkaritvā tasmā dhammā nibbijja apakkamiṃ. "
856931,164,1231,2,24,1,113,12,"372.‘‘ So kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, kiṃkusalagavesī anuttaraṃ santivarapadaṃ pariyesamāno yena udako rāmaputto tenupasaṅkamiṃ; "
