857267,164,1268,63,74,1,34,7,"‘‘ Na kho me, mārisa, so bhagavā satthā. "
857268,164,1268,75,83,1,44,6,Sabrahmacārī me eso āyasmā mahāmoggallāno’’ ti.
857269,164,1268,84,113,1,68,8,"‘‘ Lābhā te, mārisa,( suladdhaṃ te, mārisa)[() natthi( sī. pī.)] yassa te sabrahmacārī evaṃmahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo! "
857270,164,1268,114,123,1,32,7,Aho nūna te so bhagavā satthā’’ ti. 
857271,164,1269,2,14,1,57,7,395. Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
