857274,164,1269,29,65,1,116,12,"‘‘ abhijānāti no, bhante, bhagavā ahu[ ahunaññeva( sī. syā. kaṃ.)] ñātaññatarassa mahesakkhassa yakkhassa saṃkhittena taṇhāsaṅkhayavimuttiṃ bhāsitā’’ ti[ abhāsitthāti( ka.)]?"
857275,164,1269,66,77,1,69,7,"‘‘ Abhijānāmahaṃ, moggallāna, idha sakko devānamindo yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
