857279,164,1270,2,25,1,130,17,"Evaṃ vutte ahaṃ, moggallāna, sakkaṃ devānamindaṃ etadavocaṃ‘‘ idha devānaminda bhikkhuno sutaṃ hoti‘ sabbe dhammā nālaṃ abhinivesāyā’ ti. "
