857290,164,1273,2,4,1,23,2,8 . Mahātaṇhāsaṅkhayasuttaṃ 
857291,164,1274,2,21,1,87,11,396. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
857292,164,1274,22,35,1,104,13,Tena kho pana samayena sātissa nāma bhikkhuno kevaṭṭaputtassa evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ hoti–
857293,164,1274,36,52,1,99,12,‘‘ tathāhaṃ bhagavatā dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāmi yathā tadevidaṃ viññāṇaṃ sandhāvati saṃsarati anaññan’’ ti. 
857294,164,1274,53,57,1,29,4,Assosuṃ kho sambahulā bhikkhū–
857295,164,1274,58,69,1,81,9,‘‘ sātissa kira nāma bhikkhuno kevaṭṭaputtassa evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ–
857296,164,1274,70,87,1,99,12,"‘ tathāhaṃ bhagavatā dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāmi yathā tadevidaṃ viññāṇaṃ sandhāvati saṃsarati, anaññan’’’ ti. "
857297,164,1274,88,97,1,67,9,Atha kho te bhikkhū yena sāti bhikkhu kevaṭṭaputto tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
