857339,164,1276,181,198,1,89,11,"‘‘ Yvāyaṃ, bhante, vado vedeyyo tatra tatra kalyāṇapāpakānaṃ kammānaṃ vipākaṃ paṭisaṃvedetī’’ ti."
857340,164,1276,199,214,1,68,11,"‘‘ Kassa nu kho nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, mayā evaṃ dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāsi? "
