857346,164,1277,32,37,1,17,3,‘‘ Kiñhi siyā bhante? 
857347,164,1277,38,45,1,18,4,"No hetaṃ, bhante’’ ti. "
857348,164,1277,46,59,1,113,12,"Evaṃ vutte, sāti bhikkhu kevaṭṭaputto tuṇhībhūto maṅkubhūto pattakkhandho adhomukho pajjhāyanto appaṭibhāno nisīdi. "
857349,164,1277,60,78,1,168,17,Atha kho bhagavā sātiṃ bhikkhuṃ kevaṭṭaputtaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ maṅkubhūtaṃ pattakkhandhaṃ adhomukhaṃ pajjhāyantaṃ appaṭibhānaṃ viditvā sātiṃ bhikkhuṃ kevaṭṭaputtaṃ etadavoca–
