857356,164,1277,164,170,1,21,3,"‘‘ Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhave! "
857357,164,1277,171,182,1,58,9,"Sādhu kho me tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānātha. "
857358,164,1277,183,199,1,116,13,"Anekapariyāyena hi vo, bhikkhave, paṭiccasamuppannaṃ viññāṇaṃ vuttaṃ mayā, aññatra paccayā natthi viññāṇassa sambhavoti. "
