857543,164,1348,2,10,1,15,4,"‘ ‘ No hetaṃ, bhante’’."
857544,164,1349,2,25,1,138,18,"‘ ‘ Api nu tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ jānantā evaṃ passantā yāni tāni puthusamaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ vata kotūhalamaṅgalāni tāni sārato paccāgaccheyyāthā’’ ti?"
