857546,164,1351,2,23,1,94,15,"‘ ‘ Nanu, bhikkhave, yadeva tumhākaṃ sāmaṃ ñātaṃ sāmaṃ diṭṭhaṃ sāmaṃ viditaṃ, tadeva tumhe vadethā’’ ti."
857547,164,1352,2,9,1,11,3,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’."
857548,164,1353,2,24,1,141,17,"‘ ‘ Sādhu, bhikkhave, upanītā kho me tumhe, bhikkhave, iminā sandiṭṭhikena dhammena akālikena ehipassikena opaneyyikena paccattaṃ veditabbena viññūhi. "
857549,164,1353,25,48,1,136,17,"Sandiṭṭhiko ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammo akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhi– iti yantaṃ vuttaṃ, idametaṃ paṭicca vuttan’’ ti. "
857550,164,1354,2,17,1,58,7,"408.‘‘ Tiṇṇaṃ kho pana, bhikkhave, sannipātā gabbhassāvakkanti hoti. "
857551,164,1354,18,41,1,126,19,"Idha mātāpitaro ca sannipatitā honti, mātā ca na utunī hoti, gandhabbo ca na paccupaṭṭhito hoti, neva tāva gabbhassāvakkanti hoti. "
857552,164,1354,42,63,1,123,18,"Idha mātāpitaro ca sannipatitā honti, mātā ca utunī hoti, gandhabbo ca na paccupaṭṭhito hoti, neva tāva gabbhassāvakkanti hoti. "
857553,164,1354,64,90,1,149,21,"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, mātāpitaro ca sannipatitā honti, mātā ca utunī hoti, gandhabbo ca paccupaṭṭhito hoti– evaṃ tiṇṇaṃ sannipātā gabbhassāvakkanti hoti. "
857554,164,1354,91,116,1,99,14,"Tamenaṃ, bhikkhave, mātā nava vā dasa vā māse gabbhaṃ kucchinā pariharati mahatā saṃsayena garubhāraṃ[ garumbhāraṃ( sī. pī.)]. "
857555,164,1354,117,134,1,100,13,"Tamenaṃ, bhikkhave, mātā navannaṃ vā dasannaṃ vā māsānaṃ accayena vijāyati mahatā saṃsayena garubhāraṃ. "
857556,164,1354,135,141,1,44,6,Tamenaṃ jātaṃ samānaṃ sakena lohitena poseti. 
857557,164,1354,142,150,1,58,6,"Lohitañhetaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyassa vinaye yadidaṃ mātuthaññaṃ. "
857558,164,1354,151,177,1,197,22,"Sa kho so, bhikkhave, kumāro vuddhimanvāya indriyānaṃ paripākamanvāya yāni tāni kumārakānaṃ kīḷāpanakāni tehi kīḷati, seyyathidaṃ– vaṅkakaṃ ghaṭikaṃ mokkhacikaṃ ciṅgulakaṃ pattāḷhakaṃ rathakaṃ dhanukaṃ. "
857559,164,1354,178,220,1,369,35,"Sa kho so, bhikkhave, kumāro vuddhimanvāya indriyānaṃ paripākamanvāya pañcahi kāmaguṇehi samappito samaṅgībhūto paricāreti– cakkhuviññeyyehi rūpehi iṭṭhehi kantehi manāpehi piyarūpehi kāmūpasaṃhitehi rajanīyehi, sotaviññeyyehi saddehi… ghānaviññeyyehi gandhehi… jivhāviññeyyehi rasehi… kāyaviññeyyehi phoṭṭhabbehi iṭṭhehi kantehi manāpehi piyarūpehi kāmūpasaṃhitehi rajanīyehi. "
857560,164,1355,2,25,1,120,14,"409.‘‘ So cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā piyarūpe rūpe sārajjati, appiyarūpe rūpe byāpajjati, anupaṭṭhitakāyasati ca viharati parittacetaso. "
857561,164,1355,26,39,1,113,12,Tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti– yatthassa te pāpakā akusalā dhammā aparisesā nirujjhanti. 
857562,164,1355,40,62,1,156,21,"So evaṃ anurodhavirodhaṃ samāpanno yaṃ kiñci vedanaṃ vedeti sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā, so taṃ vedanaṃ abhinandati abhivadati ajjhosāya tiṭṭhati. "
857563,164,1355,63,73,1,75,9,Tassa taṃ vedanaṃ abhinandato abhivadato ajjhosāya tiṭṭhato uppajjati nandī . 
857564,164,1355,74,89,1,142,12,"Yā vedanāsu nandī tadupādānaṃ, tassupādānapaccayā bhavo, bhavapaccayā jāti, jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā sambhavanti. "
857565,164,1355,90,95,1,52,5,Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. 
857566,164,1355,96,136,1,230,29,"Sotena saddaṃ sutvā… pe… ghānena gandhaṃ ghāyitvā… pe… jivhāya rasaṃ sāyitvā… pe… kāyena phoṭṭhabbaṃ phusitvā… pe… manasā dhammaṃ viññāya piyarūpe dhamme sārajjati, appiyarūpe dhamme byāpajjati, anupaṭṭhitakāyasati ca viharati parittacetaso. "
857567,164,1355,137,150,1,113,12,Tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti– yatthassa te pāpakā akusalā dhammā aparisesā nirujjhanti. 
857568,164,1355,151,173,1,156,21,"So evaṃ anurodhavirodhaṃ samāpanno yaṃ kiñci vedanaṃ vedeti sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā, so taṃ vedanaṃ abhinandati abhivadati ajjhosāya tiṭṭhati. "
857569,164,1355,174,183,1,75,9,Tassa taṃ vedanaṃ abhinandato abhivadato ajjhosāya tiṭṭhato uppajjati nandī. 
857570,164,1355,184,200,1,142,12,"Yā vedanāsu nandī tadupādānaṃ, tassupādānapaccayā bhavo, bhavapaccayā jāti, jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā sambhavanti. "
857571,164,1355,201,206,1,52,5,Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. 
857572,164,1356,2,26,1,162,16,"410.‘‘ Idha, bhikkhave, tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā. "
857573,164,1356,27,41,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
857574,164,1356,42,50,1,83,8,So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ; 
857575,164,1356,51,55,1,51,4,kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. 
857576,164,1356,56,67,1,78,11,Taṃ dhammaṃ suṇāti gahapati vā gahapatiputto vā aññatarasmiṃ vā kule paccājāto. 
857577,164,1356,68,75,1,50,7,So taṃ dhammaṃ sutvā tathāgate saddhaṃ paṭilabhati. 
857578,164,1356,76,82,1,57,6,So tena saddhāpaṭilābhena samannāgato iti paṭisañcikkhati–
857579,164,1356,83,90,1,47,5,"‘ sambādho gharāvāso rajāpatho, abbhokāso pabbajjā. "
857580,164,1356,91,100,1,106,9,Nayidaṃ sukaraṃ agāraṃ ajjhāvasatā ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ saṅkhalikhitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ. 
857581,164,1356,101,117,1,94,10,"Yaṃnūnāhaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā, kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā, agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajeyyan’’’ ti. "
857582,164,1356,118,151,1,228,27,"So aparena samayena appaṃ vā bhogakkhandhaṃ pahāya, mahantaṃ vā bhogakkhandhaṃ pahāya, appaṃ vā ñātiparivaṭṭaṃ pahāya, mahantaṃ vā ñātiparivaṭṭaṃ pahāya, kesamassuṃ ohāretvā, kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā, agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajati. "
857583,164,1357,2,26,1,179,17,"411.‘‘ So evaṃ pabbajito samāno bhikkhūnaṃ sikkhāsājīvasamāpanno pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho lajjī dayāpanno sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharati."
857584,164,1358,2,17,1,108,12,"‘ ‘ Adinnādānaṃ pahāya adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, dinnādāyī dinnapāṭikaṅkhī athenena sucibhūtena attanā viharati."
857585,164,1359,2,13,1,71,9,"‘ ‘ Abrahmacariyaṃ pahāya brahmacārī hoti, ārācārī virato methunā gāmadhammā."
857586,164,1360,2,18,1,100,12,"‘ ‘ Musāvādaṃ pahāya musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, saccavādī saccasandho theto paccayiko avisaṃvādako lokassa."
857587,164,1361,2,28,1,144,23,"‘ ‘ Pisuṇaṃ vācaṃ pahāya pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti– ito sutvā na amutra akkhātā imesaṃ bhedāya, amutra vā sutvā na imesaṃ akkhātā amūsaṃ bhedāya. "
857588,164,1361,29,45,1,120,14,"Iti bhinnānaṃ vā sandhātā, sahitānaṃ vā anuppadātā samaggārāmo samaggarato samagganandī, samaggakaraṇiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā hoti."
857589,164,1362,2,26,1,166,22,‘ ‘ Pharusaṃ vācaṃ pahāya pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti– yā sā vācā nelā kaṇṇasukhā pemanīyā hadayaṅgamā porī bahujanakantā bahujanamanāpā tathārūpiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā hoti.
857590,164,1363,2,24,1,175,18,"‘ ‘ Samphappalāpaṃ pahāya samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti, kālavādī bhūtavādī atthavādī dhammavādī vinayavādī, nidhānavatiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā kālena, sāpadesaṃ pariyantavatiṃ atthasaṃhitaṃ."
857591,164,1364,2,16,1,96,10,"‘ ‘ So bījagāmabhūtagāmasamārambhā paṭivirato hoti, ekabhattiko hoti rattūparato, virato vikālabhojanā. "
857592,164,1364,17,96,1,724,51,"Naccagītavāditavisūkadassanā paṭivirato hoti, mālāgandhavilepanadhāraṇamaṇḍanavibhūsanaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti, uccāsayanamahāsayanā paṭivirato hoti, jātarūparajatapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, āmakadhaññapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, āmakamaṃsapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, itthikumārikapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, dāsidāsapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, ajeḷakapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, kukkuṭasūkarapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, hatthigavāssavaḷavapaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, khettavatthupaṭiggahaṇā paṭivirato hoti, dūteyyapahiṇagamanānuyogā paṭivirato hoti, kayavikkayā paṭivirato hoti, tulākūṭakaṃsakūṭamānakūṭā paṭivirato hoti, ukkoṭanavañcana-nikati-sāciyogā paṭivirato hoti, chedana-vadhabandhanaviparāmosa-ālopa-sahasākārā paṭivirato hoti[ passa ma. ni.1.293 cūḷahatthipadopame]."
857593,164,1365,2,11,1,74,8,‘ ‘ So santuṭṭho hoti kāyaparihārikena cīvarena kucchiparihārikena piṇḍapātena. 
