857612,164,1369,34,64,1,213,24,"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ… pe… tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ… pe… catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
