858013,164,1461,2,14,1,62,6,"443. Evaṃ vutte, sāleyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ–"
858014,164,1461,15,26,1,45,6,"‘‘ abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama! "
858015,164,1461,27,53,1,169,20,"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya, cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantīti. "
858016,164,1461,54,60,1,55,6,Evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. 
858017,164,1461,61,69,1,71,8,Ete mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāma dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca. 
858018,164,1461,70,89,1,67,10,Upāsake no bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupete[ pāṇupetaṃ( ka.)] saraṇaṃ gate’’ ti. 
