858020,164,1463,2,4,1,15,2,2 . Verañjakasuttaṃ 
858021,164,1464,2,20,1,87,11,444. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
858022,164,1464,21,31,1,97,10,Tena kho pana samayena verañjakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasanti kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
858023,164,1464,32,37,1,40,4,Assosuṃ kho verañjakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
858024,164,1464,38,54,1,107,12,"‘‘ samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
858025,164,1464,55,64,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
858026,164,1464,65,80,1,139,14,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā. 
858027,164,1464,81,94,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
858028,164,1464,95,103,1,83,8,So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ; 
858029,164,1464,104,109,1,51,4,kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti’. 
858030,164,1464,110,120,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
858031,164,1465,2,9,1,67,7,Atha kho verañjakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
858032,164,1465,10,16,1,67,6,upasaṅkamitvā appekacce bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; 
858033,164,1465,17,29,1,100,10,"appekacce bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu, sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; "
858034,164,1465,30,37,1,63,7,appekacce yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; 
858035,164,1465,38,46,1,66,7,appekacce bhagavato santike nāmagottaṃ sāvetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu; 
858036,164,1465,47,51,1,40,4,appekacce tuṇhībhūtā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
858037,164,1465,52,59,1,73,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho verañjakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ–
858038,164,1465,60,85,1,131,20,"‘‘ ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu, ko paccayo yena midhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjanti? "
858039,164,1465,86,110,1,119,19,"Ko pana, bho gotama, hetu, ko paccayo yena midhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjantī’’ ti?"
858040,164,1466,2,20,1,137,15,"‘ ‘ Adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhetu kho, gahapatayo, evamidhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjanti. "
