858304,164,1569,2,20,1,77,10,460. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
858305,164,1569,21,29,1,65,8,Atha kho visākho upāsako yena dhammadinnā bhikkhunī tenupasaṅkami; 
858306,164,1569,30,36,1,66,6,upasaṅkamitvā dhammadinnaṃ bhikkhuniṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
