858308,164,1569,46,57,1,31,5,"‘‘‘ sakkāyo sakkāyo’ ti, ayye, vuccati. "
858309,164,1569,58,70,1,45,8,"Katamo nu kho, ayye, sakkāyo vutto bhagavatā’’ ti?"
