858327,164,1576,2,16,1,36,5,"461.‘‘ Kathaṃ panāyye, sakkāyadiṭṭhi hotī’’ ti?"
858328,164,1576,17,54,1,255,28,"‘‘ Idhāvuso visākha, assutavā puthujjano, ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido ariyadhamme avinīto, sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido sappurisadhamme avinīto, rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā rūpaṃ, rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ. "
858329,164,1576,55,78,1,123,16,"Vedanaṃ… pe… saññaṃ… saṅkhāre… viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā viññāṇaṃ, viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ. "
