858350,164,1586,2,15,1,24,4,"463.‘‘ Kati panāyye, saṅkhārā’’ ti?"
858351,164,1587,2,19,1,72,9,"‘ ‘ Tayome, āvuso visākha, saṅkhārā– kāyasaṅkhāro, vacīsaṅkhāro, cittasaṅkhāro’’ ti."
858352,164,1588,2,17,1,71,9,"‘ ‘ Katamo panāyye, kāyasaṅkhāro, katamo vacīsaṅkhāro, katamo cittasaṅkhāro’’ ti?"
858353,164,1589,2,23,1,107,14,"‘ ‘ Assāsapassāsā kho, āvuso visākha, kāyasaṅkhāro, vitakkavicārā vacīsaṅkhāro, saññā ca vedanā ca cittasaṅkhāro’’ ti."
858354,164,1590,2,23,1,115,15,"‘ ‘ Kasmā panāyye, assāsapassāsā kāyasaṅkhāro, kasmā vitakkavicārā vacīsaṅkhāro, kasmā saññā ca vedanā ca cittasaṅkhāro’’ ti?"
858355,164,1591,2,19,1,98,12,"‘ ‘ Assāsapassāsā kho, āvuso visākha, kāyikā ete dhammā kāyappaṭibaddhā, tasmā assāsapassāsā kāyasaṅkhāro. "
858356,164,1591,20,35,1,99,12,"Pubbe kho, āvuso visākha, vitakketvā vicāretvā pacchā vācaṃ bhindati, tasmā vitakkavicārā vacīsaṅkhāro. "
858357,164,1591,36,55,1,97,15,"Saññā ca vedanā ca cetasikā ete dhammā cittappaṭibaddhā, tasmā saññā ca vedanā ca cittasaṅkhāro’’ ti. "
858358,164,1592,2,17,1,52,5,"464.‘‘ Kathaṃ panāyye, saññāvedayitanirodhasamāpatti hotī’’ ti?"
858359,164,1593,2,15,1,78,10,"‘ ‘ Na kho, āvuso visākha, saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajjantassa bhikkhuno evaṃ hoti–"
