858392,164,1613,31,48,1,147,16,"Idhāvuso visākha, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
858393,164,1613,49,57,1,48,7,"Rāgaṃ tena pajahati, na tattha rāgānusayo anuseti. "
858394,164,1613,58,64,1,44,5,"Idhāvuso visākha, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati–"
858395,164,1613,65,78,1,102,11,‘ kudāssu nāmāhaṃ tadāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharissāmi yadariyā etarahi āyatanaṃ upasampajja viharantī’ ti? 
858396,164,1613,79,88,1,79,8,Iti anuttaresu vimokkhesu pihaṃ upaṭṭhāpayato uppajjati pihāppaccayā domanassaṃ. 
