858413,164,1626,13,43,1,66,8,"‘‘ Accayāsi, āvuso[ accasarāvuso( sī. pī.), accassarāvuso( syā. kaṃ.)] visākha, pañhaṃ, nāsakkhi pañhānaṃ pariyantaṃ gahetuṃ. "
858414,164,1626,44,53,1,79,6,"Nibbānogadhañhi, āvuso visākha, brahmacariyaṃ, nibbānaparāyanaṃ nibbānapariyosānaṃ. "
858415,164,1626,54,77,1,136,18,"Ākaṅkhamāno ca tvaṃ, āvuso visākha, bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ puccheyyāsi, yathā ca te bhagavā byākaroti tathā naṃ dhāreyyāsī’’ ti. "
858416,164,1627,2,24,1,176,18,467. Atha kho visākho upāsako dhammadinnāya bhikkhuniyā bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā dhammadinnaṃ bhikkhuniṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
858417,164,1627,25,30,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
858418,164,1627,31,46,1,128,15,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho visākho upāsako yāvatako ahosi dhammadinnāya bhikkhuniyā saddhiṃ kathāsallāpo taṃ sabbaṃ bhagavato ārocesi. 
858419,164,1627,47,54,1,46,6,"Evaṃ vutte, bhagavā visākhaṃ upāsakaṃ etadavoca–"
858420,164,1627,55,70,1,77,8,"‘‘ paṇḍitā, visākha, dhammadinnā bhikkhunī, mahāpaññā, visākha, dhammadinnā bhikkhunī. "
858421,164,1627,71,91,1,121,15,"Maṃ cepi tvaṃ, visākha, etamatthaṃ puccheyyāsi, ahampi taṃ evamevaṃ byākareyyaṃ, yathā taṃ dhammadinnāya bhikkhuniyā byākataṃ. "
858422,164,1627,92,104,1,19,3,Eso cevetassa[ esovetassa( syā. kaṃ.)] attho. 
858423,164,1627,105,122,1,21,4,Evañca naṃ[ evametaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ.)] dhārehī’’ ti. 
858424,164,1628,2,4,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
