858427,164,1630,2,4,1,24,2,5 . Cūḷadhammasamādānasuttaṃ 
858428,164,1631,2,20,1,87,11,468. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
858429,164,1631,21,26,1,34,5,Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
858430,164,1631,27,33,1,12,2,‘‘ bhikkhavo’’ ti.
858431,164,1631,34,44,1,44,6,‘‘ Bhadante’’ ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. 
858432,164,1631,45,47,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
858433,164,1631,48,55,1,38,3,"‘‘ cattārimāni, bhikkhave, dhammasamādānāni. "
858434,164,1631,56,58,1,16,2,Katamāni cattāri? 
858435,164,1631,59,67,1,70,6,"Atthi, bhikkhave, dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannasukhaṃ āyatiṃ dukkhavipākaṃ; "
858436,164,1631,68,77,1,77,6,"atthi, bhikkhave , dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannadukkhañceva āyatiñca dukkhavipākaṃ; "
858437,164,1631,78,86,1,70,6,"atthi, bhikkhave, dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannadukkhaṃ āyatiṃ sukhavipākaṃ; "
858438,164,1631,87,97,1,75,6,"atthi, bhikkhave, dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannasukhañceva āyatiñca sukhavipākaṃ’’. "
858439,164,1632,2,16,1,74,6,"469.‘‘ Katamañca, bhikkhave, dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannasukhaṃ āyatiṃ dukkhavipākaṃ? "
858440,164,1632,17,25,1,58,6,"Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino–"
858441,164,1632,26,32,1,21,4,‘ natthi kāmesu doso’ ti. 
858442,164,1632,33,37,1,30,4,Te kāmesu pātabyataṃ āpajjanti. 
858443,164,1632,38,54,1,45,5,Te kho moḷibaddhāhi[ moḷibandhāhi( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] paribbājikāhi paricārenti. 
858444,164,1632,55,57,1,13,2,Te evamāhaṃsu–
858445,164,1632,58,73,1,119,13,"‘ kiṃsu nāma te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā kāmesu anāgatabhayaṃ sampassamānā kāmānaṃ pahānamāhaṃsu, kāmānaṃ pariññaṃ paññapenti? "
858446,164,1632,74,88,1,104,13,Sukho imissā paribbājikāya taruṇāya mudukāya lomasāya bāhāya samphasso’ ti te kāmesu pātabyataṃ āpajjanti. 
858447,164,1632,89,103,1,103,13,Te kāmesu pātabyataṃ āpajjitvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjanti. 
858448,164,1632,104,112,1,52,8,Te tattha dukkhā tibbā kharā kaṭukā vedanā vedayanti. 
858449,164,1632,113,115,1,13,2,Te evamāhaṃsu–
858450,164,1632,116,146,1,196,25,"‘ idaṃ kho te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā kāmesu anāgatabhayaṃ sampassamānā kāmānaṃ pahānamāhaṃsu, kāmānaṃ pariññaṃ paññapenti, ime hi mayaṃ kāmahetu kāmanidānaṃ dukkhā tibbā kharā kaṭukā vedanā vedayāmā’ ti. "
858451,164,1632,147,156,1,67,7,"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gimhānaṃ pacchime māse māluvāsipāṭikā phaleyya. "
858452,164,1632,157,167,1,66,8,"Atha kho taṃ, bhikkhave, māluvābījaṃ aññatarasmiṃ sālamūle nipateyya. "
858453,164,1632,168,183,1,88,13,"Atha kho, bhikkhave, yā tasmiṃ sāle adhivatthā devatā sā bhītā saṃviggā santāsaṃ āpajjeyya. "
858454,164,1632,184,205,1,190,19,"Atha kho, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ sāle adhivatthāya devatāya mittāmaccā ñātisālohitā ārāmadevatā vanadevatā rukkhadevatā osadhitiṇavanappatīsu adhivatthā devatā saṅgamma samāgamma evaṃ samassāseyyuṃ–"
858455,164,1632,206,214,1,31,6,"‘ mā bhavaṃ bhāyi, mā bhavaṃ bhāyi; "
858456,164,1632,215,275,1,150,22,"appeva nāmetaṃ māluvābījaṃ moro vā gileyya[ moro vā gileyya, godhā vā khādeyya( ka.)], mago vā khādeyya, davaḍāho[ vanadāho( ka.)] vā ḍaheyya, vanakammikā vā uddhareyyuṃ, upacikā vā uṭṭhaheyyuṃ[ udrabheyyuṃ( sī. pī. ka.)], abījaṃ vā panassā’ ti. "
858457,164,1632,276,312,1,214,28,"Atha kho taṃ, bhikkhave, māluvābījaṃ neva moro gileyya, na mago khādeyya, na davaḍāho ḍaheyya, na vanakammikā uddhareyyuṃ, na upacikā uṭṭhaheyyuṃ, bījañca panassa taṃ pāvussakena meghena abhippavuṭṭhaṃ sammadeva viruheyya. "
858458,164,1632,313,324,1,73,10,"Sāssa māluvālatā taruṇā mudukā lomasā vilambinī, sā taṃ sālaṃ upaniseveyya. "
858459,164,1632,325,335,1,61,8,"Atha kho, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ sāle adhivatthāya devatāya evamassa–"
