858651,164,1655,50,88,1,129,18,"Tassa te pivato[ pipato( sī. pī.)] ceva nacchādessati vaṇṇenapi gandhenapi rasenapi, pivitvā[ pītvā( sī.)] ca pana maraṇaṃ vā nigacchasi maraṇamattaṃ vā dukkhan’ ti. "
