858768,164,1678,19,32,1,121,13,Tena kho pana samayena kosambiyaṃ bhikkhū bhaṇḍanajātā kalahajātā vivādāpannā aññamaññaṃ mukhasattīhi vitudantā viharanti. 
858769,164,1678,33,52,1,108,17,"Te na ceva aññamaññaṃ saññāpenti na ca saññattiṃ upenti, na ca aññamaññaṃ nijjhāpenti, na ca nijjhattiṃ upenti. "
858770,164,1678,53,61,1,52,7,Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
858771,164,1678,62,67,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
858772,164,1678,68,75,1,54,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
