858999,164,1723,2,4,1,19,2,10 . Māratajjanīyasuttaṃ 
859000,164,1724,2,22,1,102,12,506. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhaggesu viharati susumāragire bhesakaḷāvane migadāye. 
859001,164,1724,23,31,1,64,8,Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā mahāmoggallāno abbhokāse caṅkamati. 
859002,164,1724,32,43,1,96,11,Tena kho pana samayena māro pāpimā āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa kucchigato hoti koṭṭhamanupaviṭṭho. 
859003,164,1724,44,49,1,45,5,Atha kho āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa etadahosi–
859004,164,1724,50,72,1,34,7,‘‘ kiṃ nu kho me kucchi garugaro viya[ garu garu viya( sī. pī. ṭīkāyaṃ pāṭhantaraṃ)]? 
859005,164,1724,73,78,1,18,3,Māsācitaṃ maññe’’ ti. 
859006,164,1724,79,90,1,87,11,Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno caṅkamā orohitvā vihāraṃ pavisitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
859007,164,1724,91,98,1,61,7,Nisajja kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno paccattaṃ yoniso manasākāsi. 
859008,164,1724,99,107,1,81,8,Addasā kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno māraṃ pāpimantaṃ kucchigataṃ koṭṭhamanupaviṭṭhaṃ. 
859009,164,1724,108,113,1,34,4,Disvāna māraṃ pāpimantaṃ etadavoca–
859010,164,1724,114,119,1,15,2,"‘‘ nikkhama, pāpima; "
859011,164,1724,120,123,1,15,2,"nikkhama, pāpima! "
859012,164,1724,124,130,1,42,5,"Mā tathāgataṃ vihesesi, mā tathāgatasāvakaṃ. "
859013,164,1724,131,140,1,43,7,Mā te ahosi dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāyā’’ ti. 
859014,164,1724,141,146,1,35,5,Atha kho mārassa pāpimato etadahosi–
859015,164,1724,147,156,1,45,7,‘‘ ajānameva kho maṃ ayaṃ samaṇo apassaṃ evamāha–
