859368,165,30,2,30,1,72,10,17. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ānando vesāliyaṃ viharati beluvagāmake[ veḷuvagāmake( syā. kaṃ. ka.)]. 
859369,165,30,31,43,1,102,12,Tena kho pana samayena dasamo gahapati aṭṭhakanāgaro pāṭaliputtaṃ anuppatto hoti kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
859370,165,30,44,55,1,91,11,Atha kho dasamo gahapati aṭṭhakanāgaro yena kukkuṭārāmo yena aññataro bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami; 
859371,165,30,56,62,1,55,6,upasaṅkamitvā taṃ bhikkhuṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
