859373,165,30,73,85,1,50,8,"‘‘ kahaṃ nu kho, bhante, āyasmā ānando etarahi viharati? "
859374,165,30,86,95,1,46,7,Dassanakāmā hi mayaṃ taṃ āyasmantaṃ ānandan’’ ti.
859375,165,30,96,110,1,61,8,"‘‘ Eso, gahapati, āyasmā ānando vesāliyaṃ viharati beluvagāmake’’ ti. "
859376,165,30,111,127,1,133,16,Atha kho dasamo gahapati aṭṭhakanāgaro pāṭaliputte taṃ karaṇīyaṃ tīretvā yena vesālī yena beluvagāmako yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; 
