859399,165,38,35,70,1,156,16,"Iti uddhamadho tiriyaṃ sabbadhi sabbattatāya sabbāvantaṃ lokaṃ mettāsahagatena cetasā vipulena mahaggatena appamāṇena averena abyābajjhena[ abyāpajjhena( sī. syā. pī.), abyāpajjena( ka.) aṅguttaratikanipātaṭīkā oloketabbā] pharitvā viharati. "
