859429,165,43,34,56,1,99,12,"evameva kho ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ amatadvāraṃ gavesanto sakideva[ sakiṃ deva( ka.)] ekādasa amatadvārāni alatthaṃ bhāvanāya. "
859430,165,43,57,76,1,124,15,"Seyyathāpi, bhante, purisassa agāraṃ ekādasadvāraṃ, so tasmiṃ agāre āditte ekamekenapi dvārena sakkuṇeyya attānaṃ sotthiṃ kātuṃ; "
