859432,165,43,93,123,1,128,15,"Imehi nāma, bhante, aññatitthiyā ācariyassa ācariyadhanaṃ pariyesissanti, kimaṅgaṃ[ kiṃ( sī. pī.)] panāhaṃ āyasmato ānandassa pūjaṃ na karissāmī’’ ti ! "
