859570,165,71,2,25,1,91,12,33.‘‘‘ Apāṇātipātaṃ nissāya pāṇātipāto pahātabbo’ ti iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ ? 
859571,165,71,26,33,1,45,5,"Idha, gahapati, ariyasāvako iti paṭisañcikkhati–"
859572,165,71,34,48,1,102,12,"‘ yesaṃ kho ahaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ hetu pāṇātipātī assaṃ, tesāhaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ pahānāya samucchedāya paṭipanno. "
859573,165,71,49,91,1,188,21,"Ahañceva[ ahañce(?)] kho pana pāṇātipātī assaṃ, attāpi maṃ upavadeyya pāṇātipātapaccayā, anuviccāpi maṃ viññū[ anuvicca viññū( sī. syā. pī.)] garaheyyuṃ pāṇātipātapaccayā, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā duggati pāṭikaṅkhā pāṇātipātapaccayā. "
859574,165,71,92,100,1,61,8,Etadeva kho pana saṃyojanaṃ etaṃ nīvaraṇaṃ yadidaṃ pāṇātipāto. 
