859635,165,82,19,54,1,122,12,"Tamenaṃ dakkho goghātako vā goghātakantevāsī vā aṭṭhikaṅkalaṃ sunikkantaṃ nikkantaṃ nimmaṃsaṃ lohitamakkhitaṃ upasumbheyya[ upacchubheyya( sī. pī.), upacchūbheyya( syā. kaṃ.), upaccumbheyya( ka.)]. "
859636,165,82,55,78,1,157,19,"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, gahapati, api nu kho so kukkuro amuṃ aṭṭhikaṅkalaṃ sunikkantaṃ nikkantaṃ nimmaṃsaṃ lohitamakkhitaṃ palehanto jighacchādubbalyaṃ paṭivineyyā’’ ti?"
859637,165,83,2,10,1,15,4,"‘ ‘ No hetaṃ, bhante’’."
