859726,165,110,44,50,1,18,3,"‘‘ sutaṃ metaṃ, bhante–"
859727,165,110,51,84,1,113,14,"‘ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ uddissa pāṇaṃ ārabhanti[ ārambhanti( ka.)], taṃ samaṇo gotamo jānaṃ uddissakataṃ[ uddissakaṭaṃ( sī. pī.)] maṃsaṃ paribhuñjati paṭiccakamman’ ti. "
859728,165,110,85,91,1,23,4,"Ye te, bhante, evamāhaṃsu–"
859729,165,110,92,139,1,290,36,"‘ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ uddissa pāṇaṃ ārabhanti, taṃ samaṇo gotamo jānaṃ uddissakataṃ maṃsaṃ paribhuñjati paṭiccakamman’ ti, kacci te, bhante, bhagavato vuttavādino, na ca bhagavantaṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhanti, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākaronti, na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchatī’’ ti? "
859730,165,111,2,15,1,23,4,"52.‘‘ Ye te, jīvaka, evamāhaṃsu–"
859731,165,111,16,44,1,174,24,"‘ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ uddissa pāṇaṃ ārabhanti, taṃ samaṇo gotamo jānaṃ uddissakataṃ maṃsaṃ paribhuñjati paṭiccakamman’ ti na me te vuttavādino, abbhācikkhanti ca maṃ te asatā abhūtena. "
859732,165,111,45,55,1,56,8,"Tīhi kho ahaṃ, jīvaka, ṭhānehi maṃsaṃ aparibhoganti vadāmi. "
